research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0211.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_factorized_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"16"}],"expected_win":"reduce_total_cost_into_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 u_r 是 trunk 静态向量库，b_i 是 residual 静态向量库；部署到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时可拆成 trunk 库查表加权和与 residual 库查表加权和，两部分都是静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此属于扩展兼容。r210 在 K=64、EF=1 下给出 0.69x / 0.1256，说明该 family 的质量明显优于 topk，但当前瓶颈是 trunk 带来的额外成本而非训练失稳。本轮保持 architecture、K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变，只将 TRUNK_RANK 下调到 16，目标是同时压低 encoder 与 deployment 两侧的 trunk 成本，把 total_cost 尽量拉回 <0.5x 区域，同时保留一部分 low-rank coarse 表达能力。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 TRUNK_RANK=16 能把 lowrank_factorized_residual 拉进 <0.5x 且 FVU 仍明显优于 topk@EF1,K64，则继续固定该 family，单变量扫描 K 或更小的 TRUNK_RANK 以补齐低开销前沿。","如果 TRUNK_RANK=16 仍无法进入 <0.5x 或 FVU 明显崩塌，则说明该 family 在低开销区的 trunk 分支仍然过重，下一步应回到更短链路 family，而不是继续沿 lowrank 分支推进。"],"notes_to_memory":["r210 证明 lowrank_factorized_residual 在低 EF 下具备高质量潜力，但 0.69x 的主要问题是成本而非效果。","TRUNK_RANK 是该 family 最直接的降本旋钮，且同时作用于 encoder 和 deployment，比继续调 K 更符合本轮把点拉回 <0.5x 的目标。"],"primary_variable":"trunk_rank","self_review":"该提案严格只改一个主变量，并直接针对 r210 暴露的主要矛盾：质量足够好但成本偏高。风险是 rank=16 可能过于激进导致 FVU 回退，但这是判断 lowrank family 能否进入低开销区所必需的高信息量实验。","summary":"在扩展兼容的 lowrank_factorized_residual 上固定 K=64、EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，仅将 TRUNK_RANK 设为 16，测试能否通过压缩 trunk 成本，把 0.69x/0.1256 这条高质量边界点推进到 <0.5x 区域。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0073.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 71 showed that `two_stage_residual` can benefit modestly from a higher `signum` learning rate, but Round 72 was policy-rejected because it tried to combine the optimizer test with that LR shift in a single `param_only` move. The next single mainline question remains the optimizer question, and it must be isolated cleanly from the archived reference recipe: with `ARCHITECTURE=two_stage_residual`, `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, and `LR=2.0e-3` fixed, does switching `OPTIMIZER` from `signum` to `adam` produce a healthier curve or competitive final FVU, or does this family still clearly prefer `signum`?","summary":"Stay on the `two_stage_residual` mainline and answer the optimizer question without coupling it to the recent LR finding. Keep `ARCHITECTURE=two_stage_residual`, `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, and `LR=2.0e-3` fixed at the current reference recipe, and change only `OPTIMIZER` from `signum` to `adam`. Judge this run by full curve shape against the signum reference, not just the endpoint: if `adam` is competitive and smooth, it earns one LR callback next; if it is clearly worse, keep `signum` and move on to the next recipe axis.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"mainline_improvement","family_name":"two_stage_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays on the active mainline family, respects the fixed `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` rule, uses an allowed `K`, and changes exactly one primary variable: `optimizer`. It directly fixes the Round 72 policy failure by reverting to the current mainline reference recipe instead of carrying forward the `LR=2.4e-3` adjustment into the optimizer test. The tradeoff is that this tests `adam` against the conservative anchor rather than the best observed signum LR, but that is the only policy-clean way to isolate the optimizer branch this round.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 72 was rejected on policy grounds because it coupled the optimizer change with the earlier LR adjustment; the rejection does not answer the optimizer-quality question itself.","Round 73 should isolate the optimizer axis cleanly by testing `adam` on the current `two_stage_residual` reference recipe at `K=128`, `EF=12`, and `LR=2.0e-3`, judging the whole curve rather than endpoint alone."],"next_hypotheses":["If `adam` is competitive with or better than the `signum` reference, give `adam` exactly one LR callback next within `two_stage_residual`.","If `adam` is clearly worse or noisier, keep `signum` as the settled optimizer and move to the loss or preprocess question next.","If `adam` is mixed, do not change K yet; use at most one optimizer-local LR probe only if the curve is plausibly salvageable."],"primary_variable":"optimizer"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0005.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"topk/signum 在 1.2e-3 上继续改进，说明当前主线仍未明显触达不稳定区；本轮只将 LR 继续小幅上调到 1.4e-3，检验收益是否还能延续，还是开始出现过冲与后段退化。","summary":"继续围绕 topk 主线推进，不开新 family，不换优化器，不动 K。本轮唯一主变量仍是学习率：从 1.2e-3 上调到 1.4e-3，回答“signum+topk 的更优 LR 是否仍在 1.2e-3 以上”这个单一问题。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"这轮仍然保持单变量和主线顺序，继续在已改善的方向上做最小外推，归因清晰。风险是 LR 继续增大可能引入震荡，但当前连续两轮上调均有收益，继续上探一小步比过早切 optimizer 更符合证据。若本轮不再改善，就可以较有把握地结束 signum 的 LR 扫描。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.4e-3"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 5 继续只调 LR，沿着 r3/r4 的改进趋势对 signum 做小步上探。","本轮重点观察训练曲线是否仍平滑改善，尤其是后段是否继续下降而不是出现更强震荡。","如果 1.4e-3 不再优于 1.2e-3，说明 signum 的有效 LR 峰值已接近当前区间，下一轮应切到 optimizer 维度。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 1.4e-3 继续改善且曲线稳定，下一轮可继续只调 LR 做更细化上探。","如果 1.4e-3 与 1.2e-3 接近但更不稳，下一轮应结束 signum 的 LR 扫描并只改 optimizer。","如果 1.4e-3 明显更差或出现过冲，说明 signum 的较优 LR 已在 1.2e-3 附近，下一轮按顺序切换 optimizer。"],"primary_variable":"lr"}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0007.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"A gated SAE that decouples latent support selection from reconstruction magnitude can beat the current JumpReLU anchor at K=128 by learning a separate sigmoid routing branch while staying initialization-close to plain ReLU top-k.","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["If gated shows better proxy FVU at acceptable throughput, stabilize the family by exposing and tuning gate temperature/init strength in a follow-up.","If gated quality is promising but throughput regresses, keep the family alive and do a performance-focused follow-up rather than discarding the architecture.","If gated fails to improve proxy FVU, move on to a different routing-focused family instead of more JumpReLU-local sweeps."],"notes_to_memory":["Added a new `gated` SAE family under `sparsify/` with a second encoder branch that produces sigmoid gates for support selection.","The gate branch is initialized with zero weights and a positive bias so the prototype starts close to plain ReLU top-k rather than an aggressively sparse regime.","Current execution-layer hooks do not expose gated-specific env knobs, so this first prototype relies on default `gated_temperature=1.0` and `gated_init_logit=2.0`."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"This is a clean single-family prototype and respects the proxy-first policy, but it adds a second encoder matmul so throughput may regress; that risk is acceptable for one exploratory proxy round because recent local JumpReLU tuning already failed.","summary":"Prototype a new `gated` architecture at the K=128 anchor by adding a separate sigmoid routing branch, keeping all other launch settings at baseline so the round cleanly measures whether decoupled support selection can open a better quality regime than JumpReLU.","touched_files":["/root/sparsify-ascend/sparsify/config.py","/root/sparsify-ascend/sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
