research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0090.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"After the simpler low-rank single-stage selectors (`lowrank_residual`, `lowrank_gated_residual`, `lowrank_jumprelu_residual`, and `lowrank_grouped_residual`) all failed against the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128 anchor, the most informative remaining matched architecture probe is `whitened_lowrank_residual`. It keeps the same low-rank trunk and single-stage static-library residual decode, but changes only the residual conditioning before support selection. This answers a clean question: was the mainline gain coming from the second residual stage itself, or can a better-conditioned single-stage selector recover enough quality to be worth any further attention. If `whitened_lowrank_residual` is still clearly weaker under the exact matched `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe, then the current evidence favors the two-stage residual mechanism rather than more single-stage low-rank variants.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe by switching `ARCHITECTURE` to `whitened_lowrank_residual` while keeping `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"whitened_lowrank_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This changes exactly one primary variable, `architecture`, and keeps the mainline `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe fixed. `whitened_lowrank_residual` is a coherent remaining probe because it preserves the low-rank single-stage export path while testing whether residual conditioning, rather than an extra residual pass, is the missing ingredient. The risk is that the added normalization path may still not close the gap and may be less attractive for LUTurbo runtime than the current mainline, so this should be judged strictly as a worth-continuing screen rather than a new direction to tune immediately.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"whitened_lowrank_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 90 spends the single allowed matched architecture probe on `whitened_lowrank_residual` against the exact `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128/EF12/signum/LR=2.0e-3 anchor.","Judge this run strictly as a family-worthiness probe for conditioned single-stage low-rank residual selection; the core question is whether better residual conditioning can substitute for the second residual stage.","Return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round regardless of outcome; do not treat this as license to open a new whitening branch sequence."],"next_hypotheses":["If `whitened_lowrank_residual` is clearly weaker than the matched `lowrank_two_stage_residual` anchor, discard it and resume mainline tuning on `lowrank_two_stage_residual` next round.","If `whitened_lowrank_residual` is unexpectedly competitive at matched K128, record it as a single-stage comparison point but still return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round per probe policy."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0139.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"STAGE1_RATIO","value":"0.75"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态可导出的固定向量库，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束；本轮只改两阶段预算分配，不改变 family、EF、K、optimizer、LR，也不改变最终导出形式。r138 表明把 LR 下调到 2.4e-3 会在相同吞吐和相同总 token 下把整条曲线都拉差，说明“LR 偏大”假设已基本排除；而 `adam` 在该可行主线上已有明确负信号，AUXK/TRUNK_RANK/NUM_CODES 近几轮也未给出新增益。当前尚未被回答的单一问题是：在相同总 K=128 下，将两阶段预算从默认近似 50/50 改为更前置的 STAGE1_RATIO=0.75，是否能让第一阶段承担更多粗重构，从而改善低 EF regime 的中后段收敛并把 FVU 压回 0.0581 以下。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 STAGE1_RATIO=0.75 改善终点 FVU 或曲线中后段形状，则继续在同 family 上围绕 stage budget 做更细的单变量搜索。","若 STAGE1_RATIO=0.75 明显变差，则说明低 EF 主线不受益于前置预算，后续可反向测试更保守的 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25 或关闭该轴。","若 STAGE1_RATIO=0.75 与 baseline 几乎等价，则说明两阶段预算分配不是当前瓶颈，后续应回到更贴近 deploy 成本的已知轴而非继续做 recipe 微调。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的导出形式未变，仍属扩展兼容，可继续作为 LUTurbo 主线 family。","r138 在相同 tokens_per_sec 与 final_total_tokens 下整条曲线变差，基本排除了“把 signum LR 从 3.0e-3 下调到 2.4e-3 会改善收敛”的假设。","在 optimizer 与常见 loss 轴都缺乏正信号后，STAGE1_RATIO 是当前仍未回答、且不改变导出契约的两阶段内部预算问题。"],"primary_variable":"stage1_ratio","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：只改 STAGE1_RATIO，family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 保持当前主线参考配方不变。该动作保持 LUTurbo 导出契约不变，且不应触碰 encoder 选择成本硬约束；风险是 75/25 过于激进，可能重演历史上非对称预算的负信号，因此评估时必须同时看完整曲线、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，而不是只看最终 FVU。","summary":"继续主线 family，不开新架构；在 clean baseline 与 LR 下降试验之后，转向尚未回答的两阶段内部预算问题：保持 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变，只把 STAGE1_RATIO 设为 0.75，测试更前置的 stage1 预算能否在不增加在线成本的前提下改善低 EF 主线的收敛与 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/10_20260321_011318/logs/agent_action_0002.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Run the newly added gated SAE prototype at the existing K=128 anchor to get the first quality signal on whether separate support gating can materially improve FVU over plain TopK.","summary":"Execute the first proxy run for the gated architecture family at K=128 to establish whether this new family deserves incubation.","change_type":"run_experiment","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"No new code changes this round. This is intentionally a clean first measurement of the gated family before adding family-specific sweeps or cost work.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 2 requests the first actual proxy measurement for the gated SAE prototype at the K=128 anchor.","No recent results were available, so the correct next step is to execute the new family rather than branch into further tuning.","Keep evaluation focused on FVU improvement versus the current TopK anchor; do not reward smaller K or efficiency yet."],"next_hypotheses":["If gated improves proxy FVU, do a gated-family stabilization pass on gate sharpness or magnitude defaults.","If gated is quality-neutral but slower, separate implementation cost from architectural value before discarding it.","If gated clearly regresses FVU, pivot to a different architecture family rather than spending many rounds on local tuning."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
