research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0085.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"With `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` clearly weaker than the current `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128 anchor, the next and only justified matched architecture probe is `lowrank_residual_vq`. It preserves the same low-rank coarse-trunk intuition and static-library export contract while swapping staged residual selection for a harder discrete coarse assignment. If that discrete variant cannot materially challenge the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` anchor under the exact same `K=128, EF=12, signum, LR=2.0e-3` recipe, then hard residual-VQ is not worth continuing in the current LUTurbo-aligned regime.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe by switching only `ARCHITECTURE` to `lowrank_residual_vq` while keeping the mainline recipe fixed at `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and the baseline loss/runtime settings unchanged. Judge the probe by the full curve, not just endpoint FVU: if `lowrank_residual_vq` stays smooth and materially pressures the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` anchor, it remains worth keeping in reserve; if it is clearly weaker or less stable, close the family-worthiness question and return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"lowrank_residual_vq","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This obeys the Round 85 matched-probe rule: one probe only, one main variable only, and `K`, `OPTIMIZER`, `LR`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` remain fixed. I chose `lowrank_residual_vq` because it is a genuinely different but still LUTurbo-compatible decomposition pattern with stronger prior signal than simpler selector-only families. The main risk is that hard assignment raises brittleness and may underperform on curve smoothness even if early descent looks acceptable, which is why the full trajectory matters more than the final scalar alone.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual_vq"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 85 uses the single allowed matched architecture probe on `lowrank_residual_vq` against the exact `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128/EF12/signum/LR=2.0e-3 anchor.","Interpret this as a family-worthiness screen only: because hard residual-VQ can add discrete-selection brittleness, only a clear and stable quality advantage justifies future follow-up."],"next_hypotheses":["Return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round regardless, per the operator instruction.","If `lowrank_residual_vq` is clearly worse or less stable, keep focus on mainline loss/preprocess clarification rather than reopening more architecture variants immediately.","If it wins clearly, note it as a reserve candidate but still resume mainline recipe clarification next round before any further architecture churn."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0153.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r150-r152 的 matched architecture probes 已经依次表明去掉 second stage、去掉 soft-codebook、退回 topk 都会明显恶化 FVU，因此当前问题不再是 family 本身值不值得继续，而是回到主线后重新建立一个干净的运行时与曲线锚点：在保持主线参考配方 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual / K=128 / EF=2 / signum / LR=3.0e-3 不变的前提下，确认其 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens 是否仍稳定可复现，从而为后续单变量 recipe 决策提供可信基线。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 clean baseline 复现 0.0581 左右的终点且吞吐恢复到正常区间，则下一轮再进入单变量学习率或优化器判断。","若 clean baseline 仍出现明显慢速但终点稳定，则把近期问题归因为运行时吞吐波动而非架构退化，后续 recipe 评估必须继续把总耗时与 tokens_per_sec 作为硬约束。","若 clean baseline 自身终点或曲线形状发生漂移，则先停止扩展 recipe 搜索，优先确认主线锚点后再做下一步单变量扰动。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 继续满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 已满足选择成本预算，K 保持 128，避免把部署查表成本变化与主线复验混杂。","r150-r152 的架构探针已经说明主线 family 相对近邻与简单 baseline 都有真实结构收益，本轮按规则回到主线。","评估本轮时必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时、final_total_tokens，区分是训练更长还是吞吐更慢导致耗时上升。"],"primary_variable":"other_param","self_review":"本轮不新开 family，回到主线参考配方做 clean baseline 复验，符合当前主线推进顺序。虽然这一步不直接追求更低 FVU，但在近期多轮 probe 与明显运行时波动后，先恢复可信锚点比继续做难归因的 recipe 扰动更稳妥。","summary":"回到主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，固定 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3，不引入任何新结构或 recipe 变化，先做一轮干净 baseline 复验，确认当前主线的真实训练曲线与运行代价。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0249.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"192"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"frontier_mapping","hypothesis":"候选 family: factorized_topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；低秩 factorized scorer 只改变单样本在线侧的打分与选择链路，不改变 decoder 端的单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿导出形式，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 reference_round=r246 只改一个 env 参数 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_topk`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`K=96`、`OPTIMIZER=signum`、`LR=0.003` 及其余配置不变，测试在仍显著低于 plain topk 的总成本下，适度增大低秩 scorer 容量是否能把 `factorized_topk@K96` 的 FVU 从 0.3987 明显压低，从而在约 0.25x 总成本附近补出一枚比 `topk@K32` 更有竞争力的低开销 Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `factorized_topk@K96,FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192` 明显优于 r246 的 0.3987，且 `tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens` 没有明显恶化，则下一轮继续相对本轮单变量上探到 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`，判断这条低秩 scorer 线的质量-成本拐点。","如果质量只小幅改善但运行明显更慢，则把更宽 scorer 记为负面系统信号，不再继续沿 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 上探。","如果即使 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192` 仍显著差于 `topk@K32` 的 FVU=0.3199，则关闭 factorized scorer 作为 `<0.3x` 主前沿候选，把注意力转回其他低开销 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["r246-r248 已经基本测清 `factorized_topk@FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` 的 K 轴：成本可以极低，但 FVU 始终停在 0.40+，说明当前瓶颈更像 scorer 容量而不是查表预算。","r244 说明默认更宽 hidden_dim 在 `K=96` 下能把 FVU 压到 0.3008，但成本槽位也上移；当前更高信息量的问题是适中的 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 能否在低于 topk 左端成本的前提下拿回大部分质量。","本轮必须同时比较 `val_fvu`、`tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens`；若只是质量略好但训练显著更慢，应直接视为负面信号。"],"reference_round":246,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r246 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，不联动 architecture、K、EF、optimizer 或 LR。选择回到 `K=96` 并提升 scorer 容量，而不是继续沿 `K` 轴左移，是因为 r246-r248 已经显示低 hidden-dim factorized 线的主要问题是质量而非成本；当前最小、最可归因、也最符合低开销探索目标的动作，是测试适度增宽的 factorized scorer 是否能形成更有价值的 cost-FVU 权衡。","summary":"严格锚定 r246，仅把 `factorized_topk` 的 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 从 96 提到 192，优先验证这条低秩 scorer 线能否在约 0.25x 总成本处显著提升质量，而不是继续扩展已经基本测清的超左端低 K 边界。","touched_files":[]}
