research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0020.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 19 showed that `topk/signum/LR=1.6e-3/EF=12` at `K=8` suffered a large quality drop and much heavier dead-feature pressure, with the late curve nearly flattening but not fully collapsing. This round changes only `K`, moving from `8` to `4`, to answer the single remaining boundary question: whether the current export-compatible topk recipe has any usable signal left at the absolute minimum allowed K, or whether `K=8` already marks the effective floor.","summary":"Finish the current low-K boundary sweep on the active topk mainline: keep `ARCHITECTURE=topk`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and reduce `K` from `8` to `4` to locate the hard lower bound of the present topk/signum regime.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"smaller_k","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays on the active `topk` family, changes exactly one primary variable (`k`), respects the fixed `EF=12` rule and allowed-K set, and closes the current K-only frontier scan cleanly. The main risk is that `K=4` may be clearly past the useful regime, but `command=\"stop\"` is disallowed and this is the most informative remaining single-variable question because it determines whether `K=8` is merely weak or already beyond the practical floor.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"4"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 19 (`K=8`) reached `FVU=0.380331814289093`, a large degradation from `K=16`, while late-phase improvement became very small.","At `K=8`, late `dead_pct` rose to about `0.39` and `auxk` stayed high at about `0.37`, indicating strong capacity stress and likely growing online compensation burden.","Even though the late curve nearly flattened at `K=8`, it did not fully collapse, so running `K=4` is the cleanest way to locate the hard lower boundary of the current topk/signum/EF12 recipe."],"next_hypotheses":["If `K=4` collapses or adds very little usable signal, treat `K=8` or `K=16` as the practical floor and return to non-K recipe tuning on the same family.","If `K=4` is surprisingly stable, compare it against `K=8` strictly as a deployment tradeoff point rather than against the K128 anchor.","After the hard lower bound is mapped, the next mainline question should move back to recipe tuning within the surviving low-K regime rather than continuing K-only descent."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0001.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"A JumpReLU encoder with learnable per-latent thresholds can improve the K=128 quality anchor versus plain TopK by suppressing weak activations before top-k selection, improving feature selectivity and lowering FVU without changing the execution layer.","summary":"Implemented a new `jumprelu` SAE family under `sparsify/` with save/load-compatible config support and a prototype encoder that applies ReLU, a smooth learnable threshold gate, and then top-k selection. This round should run a proxy comparison at the existing K=128 anchor using only the new architecture and its family-specific threshold knobs.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"The prototype is coherent and passes local forward/backward plus save/load checks. Main risk is throughput regression because JumpReLU currently uses a dense encode path instead of the fused topk kernel; if proxy quality is promising but runtime degrades, the next step should be a performance follow-up rather than discarding the family.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"jumprelu"},{"key":"JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD","value":"0.15"},{"key":"JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH","value":"0.10"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Added a new `jumprelu` SAE family with per-latent learnable thresholds and smooth gating before top-k selection.","JumpReLU config is execution-layer compatible via the existing `ARCHITECTURE`, `JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD`, and `JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH` env hooks in the launcher.","Local sanity checks passed for forward/backward and save/load on the new family."],"next_hypotheses":["If JumpReLU shows better proxy FVU at K=128, tune threshold init and bandwidth before considering any K reduction.","If JumpReLU quality is promising but runtime is flagged as a perf regression, fuse or otherwise optimize its encode path instead of drawing a negative architecture conclusion.","If JumpReLU underperforms badly, try a stronger routing family such as grouped or multi-branch top-k rather than continuing weak local tuning on plain TopK."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0131.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态向量库，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。本轮只回答一个问题：在 clean baseline 已稳定复现且 signum 连续多轮无改进后，改用 adam 并将 LR 联动下调到 1.0e-3，是否能带来更平滑的训练曲线和更低的最终 FVU，同时不显著恶化 tokens_per_sec 与总耗时。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 adam@1.0e-3 曲线更稳且终点更好，可继续在同 family/EF=2/K=128 上细调 LR（如 7.0e-4 或 1.3e-3）。","若 adam@1.0e-3 终点接近但明显更慢，应把它视为负面信号并回到 signum 主线。","若 adam@1.0e-3 明显欠收敛或发散，则结束 optimizer 分支，下一轮再考虑 loss/preprocess 而非继续扫 optimizer。"],"notes_to_memory":["LUTurbo 导出形式未变，family 仍为扩展兼容；本轮不是结构改动，只是 optimizer 轴探索。","EF=2 继续保证 selection_cost 在预算内；K 保持 128，不把部署查表成本变化与 optimizer 效应混杂。","r130 clean baseline 已复现当前 feasible frontier，因此可把后续变化更可靠地归因到 optimizer/LR 联动。"],"primary_variable":"optimizer","self_review":"遵守主线推进与单变量原则：family、EF、K 均固定，只切换 optimizer，并按历史规则联动重调 LR 以避免无效比较。风险是 adam 可能带来更慢吞吐或更长收敛时间，因此必须同时检查曲线形状、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens。","summary":"在已稳定复现的 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 主线上测试一次 optimizer 变化：固定 EF=2、K=128，仅把优化器从 signum 切到 adam，并把 LR 配套下调到 1.0e-3，判断是否存在比当前 feasible baseline 更好的收敛形状与 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0217.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"240"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此兼容性为直接兼容。r214-r216 已经连续证明在 EF=1 下沿 K 轴增加查表预算能稳定压低 <0.5x 区域的 FVU，而 r216 仍从 0.1635 改善到 0.1528，说明边际收益尚未耗尽；因此本轮继续在同一最短链路 family 上仅把 K 提到 240，目标是在总成本仍预计约 0.49x、继续留在 <0.5x 区域的前提下，把低开销区最佳 FVU 再向下压一截，并判断 topk@EF1 的收益是否开始真正接近平台。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@EF1,K240 继续明显改善 FVU 且运行代价未恶化，则低开销区仍可再补一个贴边点。","如果 K240 的收益很小或训练时间明显变差，则说明 EF=1 下继续堆 K 已接近边际收益极限，后续应转向新的低成本 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 目前是 <0.5x 区域最稳的直接兼容主线，且导出路径最简单，适合继续补低开销 Pareto 前沿。","r214-r216 已形成清晰趋势：在 EF=1 固定 encoder 成本下，增加 K 可以持续降低 FVU，因此当前最高信息量的单变量仍是 K 轴。","评估时必须同步比较 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，确认贴近 0.5x 边界后的额外查表预算是否仍值得。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮选择 K=240 而不是直接上到 256，是为了尽量稳妥地继续留在 <0.5x 区域，同时测试靠近边界时的真实边际收益。风险是收益可能已开始明显变小，但这正是当前需要量化的关键信号。","summary":"继续使用直接兼容的 topk family，固定 EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，把 K 提到 240，测试是否能在仍低于 0.5x 总成本的前提下，把低开销区最佳 FVU 从 0.1528 进一步压低。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0160.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终重构仍是静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 0.62x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束，并且显著低于当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的约 1.25x。r159 已经用 matched probe 说明去掉第二阶段 refinement 会从 0.0581 退化到约 0.0647，因此本轮只回答另一个互补的问题：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 与主要 recipe 完全不变时，进一步去掉 soft-codebook coarse branch、退回到 lowrank_residual，是否仍值得继续，还是 soft-codebook 分支本身就是当前低 EF 可部署 regime 的必要结构增量。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_residual 明显落后于当前主线，则说明 soft-codebook coarse branch 在当前低 EF regime 下仍然是必要结构，不应继续回退。","若 lowrank_residual 与当前主线接近且成本明显更低，则记录其为更激进低成本备选，但下一轮仍按要求回到主线。","若 lowrank_residual 意外优于当前主线，则说明当前主线 family 的 coarse branch 价值需要重新审视，但本轮仅做架构价值判断，不连续展开新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_residual 满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性为扩展兼容。","本轮严格是 matched architecture probe：EF、K、optimizer、LR 与主要 recipe 全部固定，只改 architecture。","r159 已检验 two-stage 相对单阶段 soft-codebook 的结构价值；本轮补充检验 soft-codebook coarse branch 本身是否值得保留。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把架构质量与吞吐波动混淆。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮遵守架构探针规则，只改一个主变量 architecture，并保持主线的 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变。选择 lowrank_residual 而不是更远的 topk 或 factorized_topk，是因为它是当前主线去掉 soft-codebook 分支后的最近父节点，能最干净地隔离“soft-codebook coarse branch 本身是否值得”这个单一问题，同时提供显著更低 selection_cost 的直接对照。","summary":"插入一个严格匹配的架构探针：将当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 替换为 lowrank_residual，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断 soft-codebook coarse branch 在当前低成本 regime 下是否仍然值得保留。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0033.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"The poor `gated+adam` result at `LR=1.6e-3` may reflect Adam being overdriven rather than fundamentally unsuitable, so one mandatory LR callback to `8e-4` with `ARCHITECTURE=gated, K=128, EF=12` asks only whether Adam becomes competitive when run in a more plausible range.","summary":"Round 32 rejected the optimizer swap at the matched LR: `gated+adam` finished far worse than the `signum` anchor, but that is not yet a fair read on Adam because `1.6e-3` is aggressive for this optimizer family. Per the prescribed order, the next single-variable question is the new-optimizer LR callback. Hold family, K, and EF fixed, keep optimizer as `adam`, and step LR down to `8e-4`. Read the whole trajectory: if the curve becomes much smoother and closes most of the gap, Adam was mostly mis-tuned; if it remains flat or unstable and still clearly trails `signum`, retire Adam for `gated` and move on to loss/preprocess choices.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This keeps the investigation on the same family and changes only LR relative to the immediately preceding Adam trial, which is the correct follow-up under the stated sequence. I am not touching K or opening a new family because the optimizer branch has not yet received its one LR callback.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"8e-4"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 33 is the single LR callback for the new gated+adam branch after the overdriven 1.6e-3 trial failed badly.","Use curve shape to decide whether Adam was simply mis-tuned; if 8e-4 is still clearly worse than gated+signum, retire Adam for this family."],"next_hypotheses":["If `gated+adam` at `8e-4` is still clearly inferior, revert to the `signum` anchor and probe loss/preprocess next.","If `gated+adam` at `8e-4` becomes competitive with a healthier curve, keep Adam alive as an alternative recipe but avoid broad sweeps until it actually beats the signum anchor."],"primary_variable":"lr"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0136.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"NUM_CODES","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"pareto_cost_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态可导出的固定向量库，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，已满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。本轮只改一个主变量 NUM_CODES，把 codebook 容量下调到 32，回答一个问题：在保持主线 family 与 recipe 不变的前提下，是否能以更低的 code_router/codebook_matmul 选择成本和更低的 codebook_deploy 成本，维持接近当前 0.0581 的 FVU，从而形成更强的 LUTurbo 成本侧 Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 NUM_CODES=32 仅带来小幅 FVU 退化但明显降低 deploy/selection 成本，则继续细扫更小或中间的 NUM_CODES 以压 Pareto 前沿。","若 NUM_CODES=32 的 FVU 明显恶化，则说明当前 codebook 容量已接近必要下限，回到默认配置后优先改测 STAGE1_RATIO。","若 NUM_CODES=32 与 baseline 几乎等价且吞吐更好，则可把更小 codebook 视为新的 clean baseline，再继续主线 recipe 搜索。"],"notes_to_memory":["LUTurbo 导出形式未变，family 仍为扩展兼容。","r135 的 matched probe 说明去掉 soft codebook/coarse branch 会明显变差，因此主线继续保留两阶段 soft-codebook 结构。","本轮转向 NUM_CODES，是因为它同时影响 encoder 选择成本与部署 codebook 成本，比继续做无收益 recipe 更贴近 LUTurbo 真实目标。"],"primary_variable":"num_codes","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 均固定，只改 NUM_CODES。该动作直接针对 LUTurbo 总成本中的 codebook 分支，且不触碰已证明重要的 family 主结构；风险是 codebook 容量过小会削弱 coarse branch 表达，因此必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens。","summary":"回到主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，在 EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变的前提下，仅把 NUM_CODES 下调到 32，测试是否能用更小 codebook 获得更优的 cost-FVU 权衡。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0083.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` remained smoothly non-dominated at `K=6` under the fixed recipe, so the next single-variable probe should reduce only `K` to `5` and test whether this family can extend the low-K Pareto frontier one step further before crossing the current `K=4` anchor.","summary":"Run one parameter-only experiment at `K=5` with `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`, keeping `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=3.2e-3`, and `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` fixed. Success criterion: add a new non-dominated point by landing below the current `K=4` frontier FVU (`0.14181029796600342`), with stronger evidence if it continues the smooth degradation trend from `K=7` (`0.12780356407165527`) to `K=6` (`0.13256755471229553`).","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"smaller_k","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays within the current strongest signal: one family, one fixed recipe, one variable. `K=6` was clearly non-dominated rather than a borderline near-miss, so advancing to `K=5` is a better use of the next round than a confirmatory rerun.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"5"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 83 should be a controlled parameter-only probe at `K=5` for `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` after confirmed non-dominated points at `K=6` and above under the fixed `EF=12` / `signum` / `LR=3.2e-3` / `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` recipe.","The success criterion is frontier expansion rather than a same-K comparison: if `K=5` stays below the current `K=4` anchor FVU (`0.14181029796600342`), it is a valid new Pareto tradeoff."],"next_hypotheses":["If `K=5` yields another strong non-dominated point, test `K=4` in the same family to compare directly against the current `K=4` anchor.","If `K=5` is only marginally below the `K=4` anchor, do one confirmatory rerun at `K=5` before pushing lower.","If `K=5` misses the `K=4` anchor clearly, conclude this family's useful low-K frontier likely ends at `K=6` and shift exploration to a new family or mechanism."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0028.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"With the gated K=128 EF=16 architecture now worse across all tested learning-rate alternatives, the next clean stabilization axis is auxiliary support pressure: increasing AUXK_ALPHA from 0.03125 to 0.0625 may improve feature health and residual coverage enough to recover proxy FVU without changing the core architecture or optimization regime.","summary":"Keep the gated K=128 EF=16 architecture fixed and start a gated AUXK sweep by testing AUXK_ALPHA=0.0625 in proxy.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"quality","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This follows the exploitation guidance and changes exactly one parameter on the current best full configuration after the LR bracket was effectively exhausted. The main risk is over-regularizing and diluting the main reconstruction objective, but AUXK is the highest-priority remaining single-axis quality probe within gated.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0625"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["The gated EF=16 family now appears fully bracketed on LR, so subsequent exploitation rounds should probe auxiliary regularization and other single-parameter stabilizers rather than keep shrinking or raising the step size.","This round begins a gated AUXK sweep from the best full anchor by increasing AUXK_ALPHA to 0.0625 while holding architecture, LR, and K fixed.","If higher AUXK is also worse, the remaining single-parameter gated exploitation moves are lower AUXK values or a smaller expansion-factor test rather than more architecture churn."],"next_hypotheses":["If AUXK_ALPHA=0.0625 improves proxy FVU materially, promote to full and compare directly against the current gated K=128 frontier.","If AUXK_ALPHA=0.0625 is worse, test AUXK_ALPHA=0.01 as the next milder regularization probe on the same gated anchor.","If the AUXK sweep fails at both higher and lower values, test EXPANSION_FACTOR=4 to see whether the current gated regime is over-capacitated rather than under-regularized."],"primary_variable":"other_param"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0056.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":55,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库，e(x) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。在线侧仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判定为扩展兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：r55 已证明 `lowrank_expert_residual + NUM_EXPERTS=16` 能在 <0.5x 带形成新的结构性前沿，下一步最有信息量的问题是它能否继续向更低成本带左移；相对 r55 仅将 `K: 160 -> 128`，应显著降低部署查表成本，在总成本约降至 0.46x 的同时，若 FVU 仍能维持在接近或优于 `two_stage_residual_expert`/`expert_topk` 的区间，则这条三段式 sparse-capacity 主线就会形成更强的低成本 Pareto 段。","summary":"当前不再回到 plain selector，也不继续在 `two_stage_residual_expert` 上扫预算分配。相对 r55 只改 `K=128`，是在已经出现正信号的 `lowrank_expert_residual` sparse-capacity 版本上做最直接的左移测试：保持 `NUM_EXPERTS=16`、`TRUNK_RANK=16`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 不变，仅压部署成本，验证这条主线能否把 0.49x / 0.1026 进一步推向更低总成本。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r55 只改 `K`。这不是回到 old-family 的无目的 K 轴细扫，而是在当前最有希望的新结构前沿上做一次明确的 Pareto 左移验证。选择改 `K` 而不是先改 `TRUNK_RANK`，是因为 r55 的可压缩成本更大头在部署侧，降低 `K` 对 total_cost 的影响更直接。主要风险是 `K=128` 可能削弱 residual cleanup 的表达能力，导致 FVU 回升明显；但这正是本轮需要回答的 frontier 形状问题。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual K=160 NUM_EXPERTS=16 TRUNK_RANK=16 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 已在约 0.49x total_cost 下得到 FVU=0.1026，说明 true sparse-capacity 的三段式结构在当前 target 上确实成立。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，`K=128` 时 selection 仍约 0.32x，deployment 约降到 0.14x，total 约 0.46x，预算比率约 0.31x，仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","如果这轮在更低成本下仍能维持明显优于 `expert_topk K=192` 的质量，则说明当前低成本改善不只是来自更高成本的补偿，而是来自 `lowrank + expert + residual` 结构本身的更优分工。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=128` 在约 0.46x 成本下仍维持接近 r55 的 FVU，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=96` 或 `TRUNK_RANK=8`，继续测试这条主线能否再向左延伸。","如果 `K=128` 的 FVU 回升明显但仍优于 `expert_topk`，则下一轮可回到 `K=144`，寻找这条结构线在 0.45x-0.50x 带的更优折中点。","如果 `K=128` 退化到接近或差于 `expert_topk`，则说明当前三段式结构在低成本下仍主要依赖较大的 residual lookup 预算，后续应更多测试 `TRUNK_RANK` 或切回 `two_stage_residual_expert` 做结构对照。"]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0098.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 97 showed that lowering `LR` to `1.6e-3` on the confirmed `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` K128 baseline was slightly worse, so the next single mainline question is the symmetric upward signum LR probe. Raising `LR` to `2.4e-3` tests whether this family benefits from a bit more step size for faster early and mid descent without destabilizing late training; the result should be judged from the whole curve against the archived `2.0e-3` and `1.6e-3` runs, not just the terminal FVU.","summary":"Stay on the `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` mainline and change only `LR` from `2.0e-3` to `2.4e-3`, while keeping `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`, `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, and `OPTIMIZER=signum` fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This follows the required LR-localization sequence: same family, same `K`, same optimizer, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` pinned, and exactly one primary variable changes. The main risk is overshooting a recipe that may already be near its best at `2.0e-3`, but this is the clean remaining LR question before it is defensible to close the signum LR branch and move to optimizer.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.4e-3"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 98 is the symmetric upward signum LR probe for the confirmed `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` K128 baseline after `LR=1.6e-3` regressed.","Judge this run by the full trajectory versus the archived `LR=2.0e-3` and `LR=1.6e-3` runs, especially whether the higher step size improves early or mid descent without degrading late stability or final FVU.","Only after this LR bracket is resolved should the optimizer branch open on this family."],"next_hypotheses":["If `LR=2.4e-3` clearly improves curve shape or endpoint versus `2.0e-3`, archive it as the new signum mainline LR for `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`.","If `LR=2.4e-3` is a near-tie or worse, close the signum LR branch with `2.0e-3` as the operative anchor and test `OPTIMIZER=adam` next at the reference recipe.","Do not change loss, preprocess, or `K` until the optimizer question has been isolated cleanly from the settled signum baseline."],"primary_variable":"lr"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0113.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"64"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}。其中 shared 子库 B^sh 与 routed expert 子库 {B_e} 都是静态向量库，在线侧只做轻量 router 选择少量 routed experts，然后执行 shared 查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled 结构仍明确排除。当前实际历史已在 r107-r112 上形成 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的兼容低成本前沿，其中 r111 为 0.30x / FVU 0.1228，r112 为 0.28x / FVU 0.1282。唯一主假设：在 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, NUM_EXPERTS=64` 已稳定成立的前提下，继续把 deployment 预算从 `K=80` 压到 `K=64`，有机会把 total_cost 从约 0.28x 进一步左移到约 0.27x（selection≈0.20x, deployment≈0.06x），同时仍把 FVU 控制在约 0.13 左右，从而把 shared+routed 这条新结构段继续推进到更靠左的可部署 Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=64` 仍把 FVU 控制在约 0.135 或更低，则下一轮应继续以本轮为 reference，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 或 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 之一，定位这条 shared+routed 低成本线的下一处 knee，而不是回到旧 family。","如果 `K=64` 相比 r112 明显劣化并失去非支配性，则说明当前 shared+routed 线已接近 deployment knee；下一轮不应继续降 K，而应改做 matched `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1/3` 或切回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 做对照。","如果 `K=64` 结果与 r112 接近但只带来很小成本收益，则可判定 64-80 已是当前 target 的 lookup-budget 平坦区，后续应换轴而不是继续沿 K 线性外推。"],"notes_to_memory":["截至 round 112，当前工作区真实 frontier 已包含兼容的 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 段：r107 0.42x/0.1010，r108 0.38x/0.1072，r109 0.34x/0.1147，r110 0.32x/0.1191，r111 0.30x/0.1228，r112 0.28x/0.1282。","r111→r112 已证明在 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下继续压 deployment 预算仍能形成新的更靠左非支配点，因此再做一档 `K=64` 有明确的信息增量。","本轮不需要代码修改；现有 `shared_routed_expert_topk`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 接线已在历史轮次中完成并稳定生效。"],"reference_round":112,"self_review":"相对 r112 只改一个 env 参数 `K`，满足单变量原则。继续沿 shared+routed 主线而不是回到提示里较旧的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 摘要，是因为当前工作区的 `frontier.json` 与 round summaries 已明确显示 r107-r112 形成了更新、更强的兼容低成本 Pareto 段；基于真实最新历史，`K=64` 是对 deployment knee 的最直接下一问。如果本轮不能形成新非支配点，下一轮就应换轴或换 family。","summary":"以 r112 为 reference，继续沿已验证的 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 低成本前沿做一次单变量 deployment-side left shift：只改 `K=64`，测试这条直接兼容的 shared+routed 结构能否把 Pareto 段从约 0.28x 再推进到约 0.27x，同时维持约 0.13 量级的 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0010.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"JumpReLU may still deliver a usable smaller-K regime at K=32, and measuring that directly is the highest-value next step now that K=64 stayed stable enough to earn a full run.","summary":"Run the current best JumpReLU configuration at K=32 to complete the required smaller-K exploration ladder before returning to LR, auxk, or expansion sweeps.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"cost","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"mainline_comparison","self_review":"This cleanly isolates K as the only changed variable and follows the required exploration order after the successful K=64 full run. The main downside is likely further FVU degradation relative to K=64 and K=128, but that evidence is necessary before resuming exploitation on other parameters.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"jumprelu"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"8"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"8e-4"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD","value":"0.15"},{"key":"JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH","value":"0.1"},{"key":"K","value":"32"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 10 completes the required K exploration ladder by testing the best working JumpReLU setup at K=32.","K=64 was viable enough to warrant a full run, so K=32 is now the cleanest remaining smaller-K measurement before more parameter sweeps.","This round keeps all non-K settings fixed to preserve interpretability of the K scaling curve within JumpReLU."],"next_hypotheses":["If K=32 remains reasonably competitive, return to the better of K=64 or K=32 and begin systematic LR sweeps on JumpReLU.","If K=32 quality drops too far, return to K=128 or K=64 and resume exploitation with a single-parameter LR sweep, starting with 4e-4 or 1.6e-3.","If K=32 shows instability rather than just worse FVU, keep JumpReLU and test a small auxk_alpha change on the best-performing K setting."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0044.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 43 was not a marginal win: enabling Hadamard on the strengthened `gated` anchor improved the full curve from start through end and lowered `K=128` FVU from `0.148156` to `0.142923`, while still improving late. Before treating preprocess as the new operative mainline and moving on to K, the next single question should be a clean confirmation run of the exact Hadamard recipe: does this gain reproduce under the current stack, or was Round 43 an unusually favorable draw?","summary":"Run a clean control on the updated `gated` preprocess recipe. Keep `ARCHITECTURE=gated`, `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125`, and the same runtime knobs fixed, and explicitly keep `USE_HADAMARD=1` to verify that the large Round 43 improvement is reproducible. Judge this run by the full trajectory, not just terminal FVU: if the start, mid, and late curve again sit materially below the plain-input anchor and finish near `0.142923`, promote Hadamard as the true `gated` reference recipe; if it falls back toward the non-Hadamard curve, treat the improvement as less stable and avoid overcommitting before K mapping.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays on the same family, respects the fixed `EF=12` rule, and keeps the work on the current preprocess branch rather than opening a new axis prematurely. I am not moving to K yet because the Round 43 gain was large enough that it deserves one direct confirmation before being treated as the new mainline recipe. The main risk is spending a round without frontier improvement, but the value is higher-confidence attribution of the biggest recent recipe gain.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"1"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 43 produced a substantial full-curve improvement for `gated@128` by enabling Hadamard at `LR=2.0e-3`, lowering FVU to `0.142923` with better early, mid, and late values than the plain-input anchor.","Round 44 is a clean confirmation rerun of the exact Hadamard recipe so the preprocess gain can be classified as a stable new anchor or a one-off before continuing to K exploration."],"next_hypotheses":["If the Hadamard recipe reproduces near the Round 43 curve and endpoint, adopt it as the new `gated` mainline reference and then resume K mapping from `K=96` or `K=64` downward under the improved recipe.","If the rerun materially degrades toward the plain-input baseline, keep the preprocess result provisional and avoid broad K conclusions until recipe stability is clearer."],"primary_variable":"preprocess"}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0057.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"After 21 no-improve rounds and failures from plain top-k, routed, gated, bucketed, discrete, and low-rank branches at `K=24`, the next severe-stagnation move should test a fundamentally different input-space transformation rather than another support-allocation variant. `whitened_topk` at `K=24, EF=12` may improve mid-K reconstruction by making the activation space easier to sparsify before hard selection, potentially recovering a better FVU/K tradeoff than the recent untransformed baselines.","summary":"Run a pure architecture comparison at `K=24, EF=12` with `whitened_topk` under the pinned recipe `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=3.2e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0`. This follows severe-stagnation policy by trying another genuinely different built-in family instead of any scalar sweep or code repair, while keeping the experiment anchored on the frontier-relevant mid-K slot.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"whitened_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"I avoided more support-selection and low-rank variants because those mechanisms have already failed repeatedly in this stagnation phase. `whitened_topk` is a cleaner architecture jump: it changes the input representation rather than the sparsity rule, while keeping the round architecture-only with all recipe fields pinned.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"whitened_topk"},{"key":"K","value":"24"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 57 continues severe-stagnation recovery with a pure `whitened_topk` architecture test after plain `topk` also failed badly at K=24.","Keep the run pinned at `K=24, EF=12, signum, LR=3.2e-3, AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` so architecture is the only primary variable.","`whitened_topk` tests whether input-space normalization/preconditioning helps the mid-K regime more than the recent untransformed support-selection, low-rank, and discrete families."],"next_hypotheses":["If `whitened_topk` is competitive but slightly worse at K=24, test it at K=16 to see whether preconditioning helps more under tighter sparsity.","If `whitened_topk` clearly loses at K=24, retire this preconditioned branch and move to another genuinely different built-in family rather than any scalar sweep.","If `whitened_topk` wins at K=24, follow with K=16 or K=32 to map whether the gain generalizes across the mid-K band."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0025.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"The gated K=128 EF=16 model appears sensitive to optimization, and the worse full result at LR=3.2e-3 suggests overshooting; reducing the signum learning rate to 8e-4 may improve full-run reconstruction by trading some proxy speed for a stabler optimization trajectory.","summary":"Keep the gated K=128 EF=16 architecture fixed and continue the gated stabilization sweep by testing a lower learning rate of 8e-4 in proxy.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"quality","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This follows directly from the failed higher-LR full promotion and changes one generic, launcher-safe parameter while preserving the current best architecture. The main risk is under-updating the larger gated model, but LR is now the clearest remaining stabilization axis after 3.2e-3 regressed.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"8e-4"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Gated EF=16 remains the best full frontier, but LR=3.2e-3 improved proxy while degrading full quality, indicating optimization sensitivity rather than a settled LR optimum.","This round tests a lower LR on the same gated EF=16 anchor to see whether a more conservative optimization path yields better full-run generalization.","The search remains focused on beating the K=128 gated baseline materially before considering smaller K or cost reductions."],"next_hypotheses":["If LR=8e-4 improves proxy FVU, promote to full and compare directly against the current gated K=128 frontier.","If LR=8e-4 is also worse, test LR=4e-4 as the last conservative LR bracket on gated EF=16.","If lower-LR sweeps plateau, shift to gated-specific regularization or architecture refinements instead of further generic optimizer tuning."],"primary_variable":"lr"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0190.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j；其中 low-rank trunk 库 U、静态 soft-codebook 库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都可静态导出，asymmetric two-stage 只改变 stage1/stage2 的预算分配，不改变最终 decode 仍是固定向量库上的有限加权和，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。本轮严格保持主线的 `K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3` 不变，只将 architecture 从 `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 改为 `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`，唯一问题是：在当前低 EF 可部署 regime 下，固定的非对称两阶段预算分配本身是否值得继续，还是它会在 FVU 与运行代价上都落后于当前对称两阶段 soft-codebook 主线。","summary":"插入 1 个 matched architecture probe：将当前主线 `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 替换为 `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`，其余 `K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3` 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断非对称两阶段 soft-codebook 路线在当前可部署低成本 regime 下是否值得继续。","needs_sanity":false,"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性为扩展兼容：trunk 库 + soft-codebook 库 + 两阶段 residual 字典库。","本轮严格是 matched architecture probe：EF、K、optimizer、LR 与主线 recipe 全部固定，只改 architecture。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、curve_start/mid/end、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，避免把架构质量与运行时波动混淆。"],"next_hypotheses":["若 `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 明显落后于当前主线，则关闭 asymmetric two-stage soft-codebook 分支，下一轮回到 `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 主线。","若该 probe 的 FVU 接近主线且吞吐更好，可将其记录为较低系统成本的兼容备选，但下一轮仍回到主线。","若该 probe 意外优于当前主线，则说明非对称阶段预算在低 EF regime 值得继续，但本轮只做架构价值判断，不连续展开新 family。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"本轮遵守架构探针规则，只改一个主变量 architecture，并保持主线的 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变。选择 `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 是为了在保留 LUTurbo 兼容的 trunk+codebook+two-stage 主干下，测试比 grouped/gated 更接近主线骨架的阶段预算改造是否本身值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
