research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0220.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_factorized_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是 trunk 静态向量库、{b_i} 是 residual 静态向量库；factorized residual scorer 只影响在线选择与系数计算，不改变 decoder 端导出形态，因此可直接落到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。基于 r210 已证明该 family 在 K=64、EF=1 下能以 0.69x 拿到 0.1256 FVU，当前主矛盾是 trunk 成本过高而不是训练质量不足；本轮严格锚定 r210，只改一个主轴 TRUNK_RANK，从 auto≈256 下调到 32，测试是否能把 total_cost 明确压入 <0.5x 区域，同时尽量保留明显优于同成本 topk 的 FVU。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 TRUNK_RANK=32 仍明显优于 <0.5x 区域 topk 前沿，则继续相对本轮单变量下探 TRUNK_RANK=16，检查成本-质量拐点。","如果 TRUNK_RANK=32 的 FVU 退化过大，则保留 r210 作为质量锚点，转向同 family 的单变量 K 轴或回到 topk 前沿继续补点。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_factorized_residual 的导出形式稳定为 trunk 静态库 + residual 静态库的有限加权和，满足 LUTurbo 扩展兼容约束。","r210 的质量信号很强且训练吞吐约 166.6k tokens/s、总耗时 291s，说明该 family 值得优先做成本压缩而不是直接放弃。","在 EF=1、K=64 下，TRUNK_RANK 是同时影响 encoder 与 deployment 的最高杠杆单变量；先压 trunk 比继续加 K 更符合当前 <0.5x 目标区。"],"primary_variable":"other_param","reference_round":210,"self_review":"该提案满足单变量原则：相对 r210 只改 TRUNK_RANK，其余核心配方保持不变。选择 32 而不是 16，是因为它仍应明显低于 0.5x，同时比更激进的 trunk 压缩更有机会保住 r210 展现出的质量优势；主要风险是 trunk 过窄后 coarse 补偿能力不足，FVU 可能回落到接近 topk。","summary":"相对 r210 的 lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1 做一次严格 param_only 成本压缩，只下调 TRUNK_RANK 到 32，优先验证能否把该高质量 family 推入 total_cost < 0.5x 区域。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0062.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"With the `gated` mainline stalled for nine rounds, the highest-value Round 62 matched architecture probe is `group_topk`: it preserves the same static decoder-library weighted-sum export contract and fixed `K=128`, while changing only support formation to a group-local winner scheme that could reduce selection complexity if reconstruction stays competitive. This probe answers one question only: is `group_topk` intrinsically strong enough under the matched `signum`/`2.0e-3`/`EF=12` recipe to merit any later follow-up.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe by switching `ARCHITECTURE` from `gated` to `group_topk` and keeping `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"group_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This respects the Round 62 policy: one probe only, one main variable only, and the full mainline recipe stays matched except for architecture. `group_topk` is a better probe than heavier multi-branch variants because it is directly LUTurbo-compatible and has a plausible path to lower online selection cost rather than only improving training-side expressiveness.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"group_topk"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 62 uses the single allowed matched architecture probe on `group_topk` rather than expanding the search broadly.","`group_topk` remains directly compatible with LUTurbo because reconstruction is still a finite weighted sum over a static decoder library; only the encoder-side selection rule changes.","The main deployment-relevant reason to test `group_topk` is not just FVU but whether grouped winner selection looks promising enough to justify later work on lower selection overhead under the same decoder contract."],"next_hypotheses":["If `group_topk` is clearly worse than matched `gated` at `K=128`, discard the family and return to the `gated` mainline next round.","If `group_topk` is roughly competitive, record it as a potentially deployment-friendlier selector but still return to the `gated` mainline next round per policy.","If `group_topk` unexpectedly beats matched `gated`, schedule at most one later follow-up after the mandated return to the `gated` mainline."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0115_repair_1.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"At K=24, the current two-stage soft-codebook backbone may be wasting scarce support by splitting K evenly across stages. A new `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` family that allocates more of K to the first sparse pass and keeps a smaller refinement pass could beat the K=24 anchor by using the strongest existing backbone but changing the stage budget structurally for the small-K regime.","summary":"Repaired the original experiment by completing the architecture integration chain for `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` under `sparsify/` only. The architecture string is now whitelisted in config, dispatched in `_get_sae_class()`, implemented as a concrete class with a front-loaded stage budget, and the exact smoke test passed at `architecture=lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=24, EF=12` with forward and backward succeeding.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This repair stayed within the original experiment design and fixed the actual blocker instead of redesigning the run. The registration chain is now complete and the concrete target passed instantiate/forward/backward smoke validation; the remaining risk is scientific quality, not parse/dispatch failure.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"24"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Repair round 115 attempt 1 fixed a registration-chain blocker for `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`: added config whitelist entry, factory dispatch, and concrete class implementation.","The new class inherits the two-stage soft-codebook backbone and changes only the stage budget structure, using an asymmetric split that front-loads support into stage 1.","Exact smoke test passed for `architecture=lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=24, EF=12` with forward/backward succeeding on CUDA, so the next real run should no longer fail at parse/dispatch time."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` is competitive at K=24, follow with K=16 to test whether asymmetric budget allocation helps even more under tighter sparsity.","If it clearly loses at K=24, continue severe-stagnation search with another structurally different new family rather than returning to selector, routing, or whitening tweaks.","If the full training run fails with a new runtime or autograd issue, treat that as a new blocker distinct from registration and repair the architecture-specific implementation without changing the experiment contract."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0057.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":56,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_topk"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(x-t(x)) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。在线侧仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判定为扩展兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r56 仅切到 `lowrank_expert_topk`，在保持 `K=128`、`TRUNK_RANK=16`、`NUM_EXPERTS=16` 不变的前提下移除全局 residual cleanup，可以直接回答当前低成本收益究竟主要来自 `lowrank + expert` 本体，还是来自第三段 residual 补偿；如果前者成立，则该 family 应在约 0.40x total_cost 下保持接近 r56 的 FVU，并形成更靠左的新 Pareto 段。","summary":"当前不继续细扫 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 K/ratio，而是做一次高信息量的 matched 结构对照。相对 r56 只改 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，继承已验证有效的低成本 recipe `K=128, TRUNK_RANK=16, NUM_EXPERTS=16`，直接测试在 true sparse-capacity 模式下，`lowrank + expert` 是否已经足够，还是必须依赖 residual cleanup 才能维持当前质量。按当前 cost proxy 估算，该点约为 encoder 0.26x、deployment 0.14x、total 0.40x，处于当前最需要补强的低成本带。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r56 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这不是 old-family 的局部打磨，而是对高优先级未充分验证方向 `lowrank + expert` 做一次真正公平的 matched test；相比继续压 `K` 或 `TRUNK_RANK`，这轮能更清晰地回答三段式结构里 residual 分支是否必要。主要风险是 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在去掉 residual cleanup 后可能明显退化；但无论结果正负，结构信息增量都很高，而且成本位置更贴近当前 <0.5x 主战场。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式是静态 trunk 库加单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","相对 r56 的 matched 对照可以把问题压缩为一个核心判断：当前 0.46x / 0.1113 的收益，究竟主要来自 `lowrank + expert`，还是来自附加的 residual cleanup。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=128 TRUNK_RANK=16 NUM_EXPERTS=16` 的 total_cost 约为 0.40x，明显低于 r56 的 0.46x，也低于当前 <0.5x 带的大多数结构点。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在约 0.40x 成本下仍接近 r56 的 FVU，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=160` 或 `TRUNK_RANK=32`，扩展这条 `lowrank + expert` 低成本前沿。","如果该 family 明显弱于 r56，则可较清晰地判定当前 target 上 residual cleanup 是必要组成，后续应把预算继续投向 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的更优 `K/TRUNK_RANK/STAGE1_RATIO` 组合。","如果该点虽弱于 r56 但仍明显优于 `expert_topk K=192`，则说明 low-rank trunk 本身已经有价值，后续可在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上继续做少量低成本配方压缩，而不必急于放弃这条方向。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0105.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"LATENTS_PER_EXPERT","value":"512"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 B^sh 是始终激活的静态 shared 子库，E(x) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 routed experts，所有原子都来自静态向量库，因此在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。唯一主假设：r103→r104 已证明 shared+routed 路线存在真实容量收益，但继续只扫 `NUM_EXPERTS=32->64->128` 的信息增量开始下降；更关键的问题是，在保持总静态容量扩张的同时，把每个 expert 变窄是否能把 active path 成本压回更低成本带。由于当前 `EXPANSION_FACTOR` 不能表达 `EF<1`，本轮先做最小工程接线，引入显式 tunable `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，并相对 r104 只新增这一个 env 参数 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=512` 做首轮生效验证。如果该参数真实进入 round config / checkpoint config，且窄 expert 版本在更低选择成本下仍保持可用 FVU，则下一轮再做 operator guide 指向的 matched-cost `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 结构实验。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=512` 生效且结果仍有竞争力，下一轮相对本轮只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`，做 operator guide 指定的 matched-cost shared+routed probe。","如果参数已生效但 FVU 明显崩塌，说明 shared+routed 当前收益更依赖单 expert 宽度而非更细粒度路由，后续不应继续在这条 family 上强推多 active experts。","如果 `512` 过窄，可在保持 family 与其余配方不变的前提下只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=768`，定位 shared+routed 的宽度 knee。"],"notes_to_memory":["已新增 tunable `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，并接通 `sparsify/`、`research/AutoResearch/`、`scripts/autoresearch_test.sh` 的最小必要链路；`shared_routed_expert_topk` 等 expert family 现在可以显式控制 per-expert width。","本地接线自检已通过：`validate_env_overrides` 不再拒绝 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`；shared_routed_expert_topk 在 `K=128, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=64, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=512` 下 forward/backward smoke 通过。","已完成首轮参数生效验证：本地 runner 生成的 round config JSON 与 TrainConfig 持久化出的 checkpoint config JSON 中都出现 `latents_per_expert=512`，且 reference_round=104 继承的 `num_experts=64` 仍正确保留。","resume/validation 路径也已补齐：`sparsify/__main__.py` 的 resume signature 现在包含 `latents_per_expert`，避免后续 resume 校验静默漏掉该参数。"],"reference_round":104,"self_review":"这轮先修复了 r105 的真实 blocker，而不是把 `Disallowed env override keys: LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 误判成结构结论。相对 r104 的实验语义仍只新增一个 env 参数 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，满足单变量原则；代码改动也限制在允许范围内的 `sparsify/`、`research/AutoResearch/`、`scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。我已做本地验证，确认新 key 进入 override allowlist、runner runtime config、checkpoint config 和 resume signature，不会在训练启动前再次被判为 disallowed。","summary":"已实际落盘 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 的端到端接线，并完成本地验证：新参数可被 AutoResearch 接受，expert family 可消费该宽度，`shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 round config / checkpoint config 都能正确记录 `latents_per_expert=512`。建议本轮以 r104 为 reference，只加 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=512`，先拿到“更窄 per-expert width”这条 high-information low-cost 方向的首个有效训练点。","touched_files":["sparsify/__main__.py","sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/config_resolution.py","research/AutoResearch/controller.py","research/AutoResearch/policy.py","research/AutoResearch/prompt.py","research/AutoResearch/runner.py","research/AutoResearch/rebuild_runtime_state.py","research/AutoResearch/audit_history_execution.py","scripts/autoresearch_test.sh"]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0207.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"quality_anchor_near_low_cost_boundary","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 b_i 来自单个静态向量库；在线只做单样本 top-k 选择，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时就是单库查表 + 加权求和，因此属于直接兼容。上一轮 factorized_topk 的 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM 降本尝试被 policy 拦截，且当前 <0.5x 区域 FVU 明显受 scorer 容量限制；因此本轮固定 K=64、EF=2、optimizer、LR，仅把 architecture 从 factorized_topk 切到 topk，验证去掉低秩 scorer bottleneck 后，是否能在接近低开销边界的总成本下显著改善 FVU。预计 total_cost 约 0.56x，虽略高于 0.5x，但可作为最邻近的质量锚点，帮助判断 <0.5x 区域的主要瓶颈是否来自 factorization。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@K64 相比 factorized_topk@K64 明显改善 FVU，则说明当前低开销区主要受低秩 scorer 限制，下一步应考虑在更接近 0.5x 的边界上探索更轻但非 factorized 的选择机制。","如果 topk@K64 提升有限，则说明问题主要来自预算本身而非 factorized scorer，下一步应转向新的低成本 family 或更激进的小库/小K 结构，而不是继续在 scorer 形态上纠缠。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 是最干净的直接兼容单库基线，可用于判断 factorized_topk 在低成本区的 FVU 损失到底有多少来自 scorer factorization。","本轮只改 architecture，保持 K=64 这个当前最佳 <0.5x 邻近点的查表预算不变，便于归因。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"该提案严格满足单变量原则，并针对 r206 的 policy_reject 与当前开放假设做了最小转向。代价是总成本会从 0.44x 上升到约 0.56x，不能直接补 <0.5x 前沿，但它能高信息量地判断 factorized scorer 是否是低开销区 FVU 过差的主因。","summary":"切换到直接兼容的 topk family，固定 K=64、EF=2、signum、LR=3e-3，只改变 architecture，获得一个贴近低开销边界的质量锚点，用来判断去掉 factorized scorer 后 FVU 能提升多少。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0117.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}。其中 shared 子库 B^sh 与 routed expert 子库 {B_e} 都是静态向量库；在线侧只做轻量 router 选择少量 routed experts，然后执行 shared 查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容；batch_topk、adaptive_budget_topk 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 继续明确排除。r114 已证明 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1 会明显伤害质量，而 r115-r116 已证明在 K=64、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 下缩窄每-expert 宽度能稳定左移到 0.24x/0.22x。唯一主假设：以 r116 为 reference，只把 ACTIVE_EXPERTS 从 2 提到 3，在保持 K=64、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192、NUM_EXPERTS=64 不变时，可以用“更窄 expert + 更多 routed experts”的 matched-cost 结构，部分收回宽度压缩带来的 FVU 损失，同时总成本仍约为 selection 0.20x + deployment 0.06x = 0.27x，远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，并直接回答当前高优先级问题：增加少量 active routed experts 是否比继续单纯放宽每-expert 宽度更值得。","summary":"以 r116 为 reference，保持 shared_routed_expert_topk、K=64、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192、NUM_EXPERTS=64 不变，只改 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3，测试“更窄的每-expert 宽度 + 更多 active routed experts”是否能在约 0.27x 的低成本带内形成比 r116 更强的质量点。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"相对 r116 只改一个 env 参数 ACTIVE_EXPERTS，满足单变量原则。r115 与 r116 已经连续两轮完成 width 轴的左移定界，继续压 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT 的信息增量开始下降；r114 又已经给出 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1 的负信号，因此现在切到 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3 是更高信息量的换轴，而不是重复局部微调。该点的本地成本自检已完成，combined_ratio 约 0.27，仍稳妥处于低成本探索带内。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"3"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["实际工作区低成本 frontier 已由 shared_routed_expert_topk 主导，而不是提示中较旧的 expert_topk anchor：r113 0.27x/0.1350、r115 0.24x/0.1397、r116 0.22x/0.1464 都是兼容且非支配的 shared+routed 点。","r114 明确给出负信号：在 K=64、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256 下把 ACTIVE_EXPERTS 从 2 降到 1 会退化到 FVU 0.2038，说明当前 low-cost shared+routed 质量确实依赖多 routed experts，而不应再回到单路 active path。","本地 cost 估算显示：shared_routed_expert_topk K=64 NUM_EXPERTS=64 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3 的 selection_accesses=851968、deployment_accesses=262144、combined_accesses=1114112，combined_ratio 约 0.27，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3 在约 0.27x 下把 FVU 拉回到接近或优于 r113，则下一轮应固定 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3，再只改 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT 或 K，继续做 matched-cost 压缩，确认多 active experts 是否比放宽单 expert 宽度更有效。","如果 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3 只带来很小质量改善却基本回到 r113 的成本，则可判定当前 target 上更有价值的是 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 的 width-compression 子线，而不是继续增加 routed expert 数。","如果 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3 仍明显弱于预期，则 shared+routed 在当前 target 的有效 active path 可能已经接近 2 experts 的最佳点；下一轮应换 family 或切到 matched shared+routed vs lowrank+expert 对照，而不是继续沿 ACTIVE_EXPERTS 轴外推。"],"reference_round":116}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0118.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"At K=16, the remaining gap may come from the residual coordinate system rather than support allocation alone. A new `whitened_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` family could beat the K=16 frontier by applying residual preconditioning on top of the stronger two-stage soft-codebook backbone, making each scarce activation cover more useful error directions without changing the fixed recipe.","summary":"Severe stagnation has reached 19 non-improving rounds, so another minor tweak is not justified. The latest `bucketed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` result at K=16 was close but still behind, so the next move should be a genuinely different new family rather than another routing/grouping/stage-budget variant. I would add `whitened_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` under `sparsify/` and test it directly at the more valuable smaller-K slot `K=16` with the fixed EF=12/signum/LR=3.2e-3/AUXK recipe.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"whitened_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This is a real architecture change and shifts the hypothesis from conditional specialization to representation conditioning on the strongest current backbone. The main risk is that whitening-style ideas were unstable on weaker backbones, but pairing the idea with the stronger two-stage soft-codebook family is a defensible severe-stagnation probe rather than a minor tweak.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"whitened_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"16"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 118 should satisfy severe-stagnation policy with a genuinely new family rather than another parameter-only tweak or another routing/grouping/stage-budget variant.","Implement `whitened_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` as a preconditioned variant of the current strong two-stage soft-codebook backbone so the main hypothesis is whether a better residual coordinate system helps the smaller-K lane.","Target `K=16` because smaller K is more valuable and the latest archive at that slot suggests there is still room for a new non-dominated point if the stronger backbone plus preconditioning works.","Complete the full integration chain before training: add the exact architecture string to `valid_archs`, dispatch it in `_get_sae_class()`, implement the concrete class in `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`, then run the exact instantiate/forward/backward smoke test at `(architecture=whitened_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=16, EF=12)`."],"next_hypotheses":["If `whitened_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` is competitive at K=16, follow with K=24 to see whether the preconditioning benefit persists across the mid-K band.","If it clearly loses at K=16, continue severe-stagnation search with another genuinely different new family rather than more soft-codebook conditional or stage-budget variants.","If the smoke test passes but full training fails, repair the new architecture-specific blocker without changing the family or env overrides."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/logs/agent_action_0032.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Crash recovery mode requires returning to the best known working family and making only a small stable parameter change. The recent lowrank_gated_residual sweeps showed that higher LR, added aux pressure, and larger EF all regress at K=128, so the clean remaining stability-oriented probe is to reduce only `EXPANSION_FACTOR` from 32 to 16 on the same winning signum recipe and test whether the family is over-parameterized at the anchor.","summary":"Run a proxy stabilization pass for `lowrank_gated_residual` at K=128 with `EXPANSION_FACTOR=16`, holding architecture, optimizer, LR, aux, and batch settings fixed. This is a param-only recovery round on the best working configuration, aimed at checking whether a smaller residual dictionary improves stability or quality while also reducing cost.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"lowrank_gated_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This follows crash recovery mode by avoiding code edits and new architectures, and it stays on the strongest proven family with a single minor parameter adjustment. The choice also matches the remaining untested low-risk branch after the EF=48, LR, and aux probes all regressed.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_gated_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"HOOKPOINTS","value":"layers.[3].self_attn.o_proj"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Crash recovery mode forced a return to param-only search on the best working family, `lowrank_gated_residual`, with no code edits.","After regressions from higher LR, nonzero aux, and larger EF, the remaining low-risk probe is to reduce `EXPANSION_FACTOR` below the current EF=32 default at K=128.","This round also tests whether the winning family can retain anchor quality with lower dictionary capacity and better cost/stability characteristics."],"next_hypotheses":["If `EXPANSION_FACTOR=16` improves proxy FVU or holds quality with better runtime, promote it to full and then compare the same EF at K=64.","If EF=16 is flat or worse, keep EF=32 as the mainline default and continue crash recovery with another minor param-only probe such as `EXPANSION_FACTOR=4` rather than changing architecture.","If EF=16 improves throughput materially but loses only a little quality, consider it as a Pareto-strengthening cost point even if it does not beat the best K=128 FVU."],"primary_variable":"expansion_factor"}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0029.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Five non-improving rounds on gated-specific tweaks suggest the current search direction is locally exhausted, so the next meaningful move is to revisit a fundamentally different sparse selection mechanism. A clean top-k mainline comparison at K=128 using the current strongest training regime may show whether gated-specific routing is the bottleneck rather than the optimizer or regularization settings.","summary":"Return to the incubating top-k family and run a proxy architecture comparison at K=128 under the current best gated training settings.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"quality","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline_comparison","self_review":"This satisfies the mandatory mode shift away from minor gated sweeps and makes one coherent architecture change while keeping the rest of the regime fixed. The main risk is that top-k was already only moderately competitive in an earlier proxy, but it is the cleanest fundamentally different architecture available without adding more code churn during severe stagnation.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Five consecutive non-improving rounds indicate the gated-local search is exhausted for now and require a shift to a fundamentally different architecture path.","This round reopens the incubating top-k family under the current strongest gated training regime so the architecture comparison is clean and current.","Using the best validated optimizer and capacity settings isolates whether the selection mechanism itself is limiting quality rather than stale hyperparameters from the earlier top-k probe."],"next_hypotheses":["If top-k proxy FVU improves materially over its earlier result and is competitive with gated, promote it to full and begin top-k stabilization from this stronger anchor.","If top-k remains clearly worse even under the stronger regime, conclude that a different architectural direction is needed and retire top-k from near-term focus.","If top-k is competitive on quality but notably better on runtime or stability, keep it alive as an alternate mainline family for subsequent cost-quality tradeoff work."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0118.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}。其中 shared 子库 B^sh 与 routed expert 子库 {B_e} 都是静态向量库；在线侧只做轻量 router 选择少量 routed experts，然后执行 shared 查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容；batch_topk、adaptive_budget_topk 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 继续明确排除。r117 已经给出负信号：在 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` 下，把额外预算花在 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3` 上，只把 FVU 从 0.1464 小幅拉到 0.1440，却回到约 0.27x 成本，未形成新前沿。唯一主假设：以 r116 为 reference，只把 `K` 从 64 提到 80，在保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 不变时，若质量主要受限于在线查表容量而不是 routed expert 数，那么这 0.01x 左右的额外部署预算会比 r117 的 active-path 扩张更有效地回收 FVU，使该点在约 selection 0.16x + deployment 0.08x = total 0.23x 的低成本带内形成比 r116 更强、且优于“加一个 routed expert”的 matched-cost 对照。","summary":"以 r116 为 reference，保持 `shared_routed_expert_topk`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 不变，只改 `K=80`，直接比较“加少量 lookup budget”是否比 r117 的“加 routed expert”更值得。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"相对 r116 只改一个 env 参数 `K`，满足单变量原则。r117 已经回答了 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3` 这条轴的主要问题且结果偏负，因此本轮改做 deployment 轴，是合规的换轴而不是重复微调。选择 `K=80` 而不是回到更高成本点，是因为本地 cost 自检显示该点 combined_ratio 约 0.23，仍处于当前最需要补强的低成本带，同时它与 r115/r116/r117 构成很干净的 matched-cost 对照：同样是给 r116 补一点预算，本轮把预算给查表容量，不再给更多 active experts。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"80"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["实际工作区低成本 frontier 已由 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 主导：r113 约 0.27x / FVU 0.1350，r115 约 0.24x / 0.1397，r116 约 0.22x / 0.1464；提示中的 `<0.5x` 摘要已明显过时。","r117 给出清晰负信号：`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3` 在 `K=64, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` 下仅把 FVU 从 0.1464 改到 0.1440，但成本抬回约 0.27x，说明在当前 target 上继续增加 routed expert 数的边际收益很弱。","本地 cost 估算显示：`shared_routed_expert_topk K=80 NUM_EXPERTS=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` 的 selection_accesses=655360、deployment_accesses=327680、combined_accesses=983040，combined_ratio 约 0.23，明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=80` 在约 0.23x 下把 FVU 明显拉回到接近 r115，说明对当前窄 expert recipe 来说，额外预算更该给 lookup capacity 而不是更多 active routed experts；下一轮可继续在 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下细化 `K=72/80/96` 的 deployment knee。","如果 `K=80` 仍只带来很小改善，则说明 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` 这条 width-compression 子线已经接近质量下限，shared+routed 方向在当前 target 的低成本增益基本摸清；下一轮应换 family，而不是继续扫同一子线。","如果 `K=80` 意外接近或优于 r115，则可以判定‘窄 expert + 稍多 lookup’比‘更宽 expert + 更少 lookup’更有效；后续应优先做 matched `K`/`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 交换，而不是再碰 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3`。"],"reference_round":116}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0114.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"At K=24, `whitened_lowrank_residual` may recover a better mid-K tradeoff than the recent selector/routing misses by preconditioning the low-rank residual before top-k selection, improving support quality without changing the fixed recipe.","summary":"Severe stagnation is active and K coverage is already broad, so the next move should be a fundamentally different built-in architecture rather than another minor tweak. I chose an untested-in-loop family already present in `sparsify/`: `whitened_lowrank_residual`. It directly targets the idea-bank hypothesis that a better residual coordinate system can help low-K coding, while keeping the comparison clean at the smaller, frontier-relevant K=24 slot.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"whitened_lowrank_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This is a real architecture change with a single hypothesis and minimal overrides. The main risk is prior whitening-style variants were unstable or weak, but this specific low-rank residual preconditioner has not been given a controlled K=24 trial in the current loop.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"whitened_lowrank_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"24"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 114 should satisfy severe-stagnation policy with a fundamentally different built-in family rather than another selector tweak.","`whitened_lowrank_residual` is already registered in `sparsify/config.py` and `_get_sae_class()`; this round is parameter-only, but mark sanity required because the family has not been run in the current controlled loop.","Keep the override set minimal and exact so the result is attributable to architecture alone at the frontier-relevant K=24 slot."],"next_hypotheses":["If `whitened_lowrank_residual` is competitive at K=24, follow with K=16 to test whether residual preconditioning helps more under tighter sparsity.","If it clearly loses at K=24, continue severe-stagnation search with another structurally different existing family rather than more selector/routing variants.","If it is noisy but close at K=24, run one confirmatory repeat before promoting or discarding the family."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0090.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{e∈E(z(x))} Σ_{i∈S_e(z(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 z(x)=Bx 是共享低维投影，E(z) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 active experts，expert 内用小型 low-rank head A_e z 做 local scoring/top-k，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。在线侧可直接导出为“shared low-rank projection + 少量静态 expert 子库选择 + 子库内查表 + 有限加权求和”的 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `factorized_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r86 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_topk` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，在保持 `K=128`、`NUM_EXPERTS=16`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，如果 r86 的失败主要来自 full-dim routed scorer 太重而不是 multi-expert MoE-like 本身，那么 shared-basis expert routing 应能在更低 total_cost 下显著改善 FVU，并在 0.3x 左右成本带形成新的结构性 anchor。按当前成本模型粗估，selection≈0.19x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.31x，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","summary":"Round 90 不继续沿 r86 的旧实现轴细扫，而是做一个更高信息量的 matched architecture swap：以 r86 为 reference，只改成 `factorized_expert_topk`。这直接回答“multi-expert active path 的问题是在 MoE 结构本身，还是在 full-dim scorer 太重”这个当前低成本前沿最关键的结构问题。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r86 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这一步比继续调 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 或 `NUM_EXPERTS` 更有信息量，因为它在保留同一 multi-expert MoE-like 语义下，把 scorer 从全维 routed head 换成 shared low-rank basis，能更干净地区分瓶颈来源。主要风险是该 family 在当前 target 上可能训练稳定性不足；因此保留 sanity 更稳妥。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["这轮是对 r86 负结果的结构归因实验：保持 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 与 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 不变，只把 routed scorer 换成 shared-basis low-rank head。","`factorized_expert_topk` 的最终形式仍是静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和；共享投影只改变在线选择链路，不引入动态字典，因此兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 粗估，`factorized_expert_topk K=128 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=16 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 的 total_cost 约 0.31x，明显低于 r86 所在成本带，也落在当前最需要补强的低成本区间。","如果该 family 在近 0.31x 成本下仍明显不优于当前 low-cost anchors，则 shared-basis expert routing 这条线在当前 target 上应降低优先级。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 在约 0.31x total_cost 下显著优于 r86 并接近当前 <0.5x 前沿，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=32`，验证 shared-basis MoE-like 的容量扩张是否继续成立。","如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 有正信号但仍弱于预期，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，区分瓶颈是在 shared basis 宽度还是在 routed capacity。","如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 仍然表现很差，则说明当前 target 上 multi-expert routed-only 路线整体不值得继续，后续应把低成本结构预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert`。"],"reference_round":86}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0067.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"The best existing promoted alternatives have now been refreshed and still sit well behind the gated frontier, so the least-bad next informative move is a genuinely new architecture family rather than another local sweep. A `lowrank_residual` SAE that uses a learned low-rank linear trunk plus a sparse residual coder could remove shared dense structure before TopK selection, which is a materially different way to attack the K=128 quality ceiling without changing the execution layer.","summary":"Add a `lowrank_residual` prototype under `sparsify/` and run a K=128 proxy comparison under the current strongest signum regime.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"lowrank_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This is a clean architecture exploration step after both gated and refreshed JumpReLU evidence failed to reopen the mainline frontier. The main risk is prototype underperformance, but the proposed family tests a genuinely different structural hypothesis rather than repeating exhausted sparse-mechanism variants.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 66 refreshed the strongest non-gated legacy family and it remained far from the gated anchor, so the promoted existing alternatives should now be treated as close to exhausted.","The next search step should test a structurally different hypothesis rather than another local change to gating, thresholds, or optimizer.","A low-rank-trunk plus sparse-residual encoder directly targets the possibility that the activation space contains a shared dense component that current flat sparse coders are wasting K to model."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_residual` runs and shows competitive proxy FVU, keep the family alive and stabilize its trunk width next.","If it runs cleanly but is clearly worse than gated and not better than prior archived families, archive it quickly and move to another genuinely new family.","If it fails at sanity or selection, treat that as an architecture-compatibility blocker and do one narrow code-fix follow-up before judging the family."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0003.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 2 的 6e-4 明显劣于 8e-4，说明当前 topk/signum 主线更像是欠步长而不是过冲；本轮只把学习率上调到 1e-3，检验更积极的步长是否能在相同 family/optimizer/K 下带来更快且仍稳定的收敛，并刷新 K=128 的 FVU。","summary":"继续围绕 topk 主线推进，不开新 family，不换优化器，不动 K。本轮唯一主变量仍是 LR：从参考配方 8e-4 上调到 1e-3，回答“signum+topk 在当前设置下是否更需要稍大的学习率”这个单一问题。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"这轮保持单变量且遵循主线顺序，先把 LR 维度补全到高于 baseline 的一侧，再决定是否切 optimizer。风险是 1e-3 可能带来震荡，但这正是本轮要验证的核心问题；若曲线恶化，后续就有充分理由结束 signum 的 LR 扫描并转向 optimizer 对比。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1e-3"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 3 继续只调 LR，补完 signum 在 baseline 以上一侧的步长测试。","r2 的 6e-4 比 baseline 更差，初步说明问题不像是 LR 过大，更可能是步长偏小导致收敛不足。","本轮重点看曲线是否出现更快下降且仍稳定；若 1e-3 出现明显震荡或最终更差，就可结束 signum 的主线 LR 扫描并转向 optimizer 比较。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 1e-3 优于 8e-4，下一轮继续只调 LR，在 8e-4 到 1e-3 之间或略高处做细化。","如果 1e-3 与 8e-4 接近但更不稳，下一轮可结束 signum 的 LR 扫描，按顺序只改 optimizer。","如果 1e-3 明显更差且有震荡，说明 signum 的合适 LR 区间已基本摸清，下一轮应切到 optimizer 维度。"],"primary_variable":"lr"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0145.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.3e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 静态库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 静态字典库 {b_i} 都可离线导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r144 已重新确认当前主线参考配方可稳定复现 0.0581 附近 FVU 且运行代价恢复正常，因此现在应按顺序回到单变量学习率轴，而不是继续做架构探针或过早切换 optimizer。本轮只回答一个问题：在保持 family、EF、K、optimizer 全不变的前提下，将 signum 的 LR 从 3.0e-3 小幅上调到 3.3e-3，是否能在不明显恶化 tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens 的情况下，改善中后段收敛形状并把 FVU 压到 0.0581 以下。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 LR=3.3e-3 在曲线中后段与终点上优于 3.0e-3，且运行代价基本不变，则继续围绕 signum 做小步上探或复验。","若 LR=3.3e-3 与 baseline 基本等价或更差，则说明 3.0e-3 已接近当前 signum 最优点，后续应关闭 LR 轴并转向 optimizer 或成本轴。","若 LR=3.3e-3 只带来极小 FVU 变化但明显拖慢训练或拉长总时长，则将其视为负面 recipe 信号，不再继续上探。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 仍是当前兼容 frontier 上质量最强的可行主线，导出形式未变，继续属于扩展兼容。","r144 clean baseline 已重新确认主线参考配方稳定，因此后续 recipe 变化可以更可靠地归因到单变量本身。","学习率轴此前表明 2.4e-3 偏低、3.6e-3 未带来收益；3.3e-3 是对 3.0e-3 的最小上探，用于判断是否仍有轻微的 signum 步长余量。"],"primary_variable":"lr","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：只改 LR，family、EF、K、optimizer 与导出形式全部固定，不混入成本轴或 loss 轴变化。该动作符合当前推荐顺序，在 EF 成本可行且 clean baseline 已补齐后，先完成更细的 LR 局部搜索。风险是 3.3e-3 可能只会带来更激进但无收益的更新，因此评估时必须同时看完整曲线、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，而不是只看最终 FVU。","summary":"继续围绕当前主线 family 推进，不开新 family；在 r144 已恢复 clean baseline 锚点后，本轮进入单变量 LR 微调，保持 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum 不变，只把 LR 从 3.0e-3 小幅上调到 3.3e-3，测试是否能改善中后段收敛并刷新当前可行 frontier。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0114.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","reference_round":113,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}。其中 shared 子库 B^sh 与 routed expert 子库 {B_e} 都是静态向量库，在线侧只做轻量 router 选择少量 routed experts，然后执行 shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 继续明确排除。r107-r113 已经证明 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 在 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下形成了真实低成本 Pareto 段，并在 r113 达到约 0.27x / FVU 0.1350。唯一主假设：在 `K=64, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64` 固定时，把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，会把 selection cost 从约 0.20x 降到约 0.14x、total_cost 从约 0.27x 左移到约 0.20x，同时若 FVU 仍明显优于当前直接兼容 cost anchor `expert_topk K=128` 的 0.3149，则可以回答“shared+routed 的低成本收益是否真的需要双 routed experts”，并在更低成本带建立新的结构性 anchor。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 在约 0.20x total_cost 下仍把 FVU 压到约 0.20 或更低，则下一轮应以本轮为 reference，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 或 `K`，继续细化这条更便宜的 shared+routed 子线。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 明显退化而劣于 r113 太多，则说明当前 shared+routed 前沿的质量确实依赖双 routed experts；下一轮不应继续压 active path，而应回到 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 主线换轴。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 与 r113 接近但成本显著更低，则可判定当前 target 上 shared+routed 的主要收益来自 shared+routed 分解本身，而不完全来自多 routed experts。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 selection cost 自检显示：`shared_routed_expert_topk K=64 NUM_EXPERTS=64 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 的 selection ratio 约 0.14x、deployment ratio 约 0.06x、combined ratio 约 0.20x；对应 r113 baseline (`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`) 为约 0.27x。","r107-r113 已经把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 的 shared+routed 低成本线推到 0.42x→0.27x；当前最有信息量的问题不再是继续线性降 K，而是这条线在更低 encoder 成本下是否仍成立。","本轮不需要代码修改；`ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 与 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 wiring 已在历史轮次中稳定生效。"],"self_review":"相对 r113 只改一个 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，满足单变量原则。之所以不继续沿 `K` 轴外推，是因为 r112→r113 已经连续两轮回答 deployment knee，并且都形成了新非支配点；当前更高信息量的是切换到 active-path 轴，直接比较当前 low-cost shared+routed 前沿对双 routed experts 的依赖程度。该点仍远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","summary":"以 r113 为 reference，保持 `shared_routed_expert_topk`、`K=64`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 不变，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，测试 shared+routed 在约 0.20x total_cost 下是否仍能显著优于旧 `expert_topk` 低成本锚点，并回答当前低成本收益是否真的依赖双 routed experts。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0032.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i。对 `jumprelu` 而言，threshold 与 bandwidth 只改变支持集 S(x) 的形成方式，decoder 仍是同一个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的查表 + 加权求和链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。r29-r31 已表明 `jumprelu` 在 0.44x 成本带能与当前 best <0.5x 点基本持平并略优，因此下一步最有信息量的动作不是继续改门控细节，而是在保持同 family 与同配方的前提下只增大 K 到 224，把总成本推到约 0.47x，测试它能否在仍低于 0.5x 的区域内给出更明确的 FVU 改善。","summary":"基于 r31 的 jumprelu 配方做一次低开销前沿扩展：仅把 K 从 192 提到 224，保持 ARCHITECTURE=jumprelu、EF=1、JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD=0.05、JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH=0.05、adam、8e-4 不变，验证该 family 能否在约 0.47x total_cost 下补出优于当前 <0.5x 最佳点的新 Pareto 点。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"主要风险是 K=224 只带来很小的 FVU 改善，不足以抵消部署成本上升，从而形成一个被现有 0.44x 点近似支配的弱点；但在 jumprelu 已经出现 matched-cost 正信号的前提下，这一步能直接回答该 family 是否值得占据 <0.5x 主线。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"224"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["jumprelu 当前是唯一在 0.44x 成本带对 topk K=192 给出微弱正信号的已测兼容 family。","在当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，jumprelu K=224 EF=1 的预估成本约为 encoder 0.25x + deploy 0.22x = total 0.47x，仍处于本阶段重点的 <0.5x 区域。","本轮改 K 而不改门控参数，用于判断 jumprelu 的收益是否能沿低成本 Pareto 前沿继续放大。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 jumprelu K=224 明显优于当前 best <0.5x 点，则下一轮优先在该 family 内继续做少量 K 邻域刻画，确认低成本前沿形状。","如果 K=224 仍只给出边际改善或无改善，则停止继续打磨 jumprelu，转向新的兼容 family 或新的结构槽位。"],"reference_round":31}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0171.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"After 30 non-improving rounds and two failed non-architecture probes on the current `K=32` anchor, the next policy-compliant move is to test a fundamentally different existing family at another frontier-relevant small budget. `lowrank_gated_residual` is the strongest non-codebook prior at larger K, so probing it at `K=64, EF=16` under the modern pinned signum recipe tests whether a simpler gated sparse mechanism can recover a non-dominated mid-K tradeoff where the current bucketed soft-codebook backbone may be over-specialized.","summary":"Run an architecture-only comparison at `K=64, EF=16` by switching from `bucketed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` to `lowrank_gated_residual` while keeping optimizer, LR, aux loss, and preprocessing fixed. This satisfies the severe-stagnation requirement to stop minor tweaks and try a fundamentally different architecture, while targeting a strategically useful smaller-K frontier slot rather than spending another round on the already-stressed `K=32` lane.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"lowrank_gated_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This round changes only architecture relative to the pinned modern recipe, so attribution stays clean. I chose `K=64` instead of `K=32` because repeated `K=32` probes have been unproductive and `lowrank_gated_residual` historically improves as K rises, making `K=64` the better chance for a new non-dominated point under the enforced `EF=16` regime.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_gated_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 171 returns to an architecture-only move because severe stagnation policy now explicitly requires a fundamentally different architecture after failed preprocessing and loss probes.","`lowrank_gated_residual` at `K=64, EF=16` is the selected probe because gating is materially different from the current codebook backbone and historically strengthens at higher K more than at `K=24/32`."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_gated_residual` is competitive at `K=64, EF=16`, follow with `K=96` on the same family to map whether the gated residual lane can replace the current high-quality anchor family under the fixed EF=16 constraint.","If it is clearly worse but trains smoothly, keep the family in reserve for a later optimizer probe with Adam plus a deliberately chosen LR retune rather than discarding the optimizer-family pairing from a signum-only result.","If it fails badly, continue severe-stagnation architecture search with another fundamentally different existing family rather than returning to more minor recipe changes."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0031.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Within the `gated` mainline at `K=128, EF=12, optimizer=signum`, a conservative LR step down from `1.6e-3` to `1.2e-3` may improve stability and early-to-mid training curve smoothness enough to beat the current `0.149866` result; this round asks only whether the matched `gated` recipe is slightly overdriven at the reference LR.","summary":"Round 30's clean-baseline proposal was rejected by policy, so the next valid mainline move is the first LR callback while holding family, K, EF, and optimizer fixed. This stays on `gated`, changes only LR, and is explicitly aimed at reading the curve shape: if `1.2e-3` descends more smoothly and avoids late flattening or noise while matching or improving terminal FVU, keep sweeping LR inside `gated`; if it is simply slower and worse throughout, the reference LR remains the right anchor.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"small","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This obeys the one-variable rule by changing only LR, keeps EF at 12 and K at 128, and follows the prescribed mainline order after the clean-baseline step was unavailable. I am not changing optimizer yet because LR remains the highest-value unresolved variable inside the current gated recipe.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.2e-3"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 31 starts the gated LR sweep because the clean-baseline rerun was policy-rejected; first callback is downward to LR=1.2e-3 with all other recipe fields fixed.","Judge the run by trajectory shape as well as terminal FVU: smoother monotone descent with equal/better finish supports gated at lower LR; uniformly slower/worse suggests 1.6e-3 was already near-correct."],"next_hypotheses":["If `gated` at LR=1.2e-3 is smoother and at least as good, try one upward/downward bracket endpoint next to localize the LR optimum.","If `gated` at LR=1.2e-3 is clearly worse across the curve, keep `1.6e-3` as the gated anchor and consider optimizer swap next."],"primary_variable":"lr"}
