research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0051.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Stability has returned on the gated path, and the K=64 point was reconfirmed exactly in both proxy and full. The next least-risk informative move is to refresh the adjacent lower-cost gated Pareto point at K=32 under the same strongest regime, keeping architecture, optimizer, LR, AUXK, and expansion fixed so only K changes.","summary":"Run a gated proxy stabilization pass on the current best EF=16 signum configuration with `K=32`, keeping LR=1.6e-3 and AUXK_ALPHA=0.01 fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This keeps the session on the stable best-known family, changes only one parameter, and updates the next lower-K Pareto point after K=64 was reconfirmed cleanly. The main risk is low novelty because K=32 is already on the frontier, but it is still the safest informative move before reintroducing any blocked architecture work.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.01"},{"key":"K","value":"32"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 50 restored a clean working baseline: gated K=64 reproduced its prior proxy and full behavior under the strongest stable regime.","This round stays on the same gated recipe and changes only K, moving to the adjacent lower-cost Pareto point at K=32.","After repeated factorized-topk crashes, continued progress should come from stable gated runs until there is a concrete implementation plan for any new architecture attempt."],"next_hypotheses":["If K=32 matches or improves its prior proxy behavior, keep the gated low-K frontier confirmed and consider cost-focused comparisons within the stable family.","If K=32 regresses unexpectedly under the same stable recipe, treat recent results as noisy and return to the exact K=128 anchor to recheck baseline stability.","If stability remains clean after this round, resume broader architecture exploration only with an implementation plan that avoids the recent unregistered-architecture failure mode."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0100.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":99,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r_1)} γ_j(x) c_j，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r 是共享 low-rank trunk，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，r_1 = x - t(x) - Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单个静态 expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属于直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r98 在 `K=96`、r99 在 `K=112` 上连续给出清晰正斜率，说明当前压缩版三段式结构仍然受 deployment lookup budget 限制，而不是已经在 `K=96` 附近饱和。相对 r99 仅将 `K: 112 -> 128`，在保持 `TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变时，如果这条 family 的收益继续随 K 增长，那么 FVU 应进一步低于 r99 的 0.0973，并完成当前 `lowrank_expert_residual` deployment knee 的上沿定位。","summary":"r98 和 r99 已经把压缩版 `lowrank_expert_residual` 从 `K=96` 推到 `K=112` 且持续改善，因此本轮不切 family，也不回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或 routed-only 方向。以 r99 为 reference，只改 `K=128`，直接回答这条三段式主线在当前 recipe 下的 deployment budget 是否仍有显著质量收益，并完成 `K=96-128` 的上沿定位。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r99 只改 `K`。这不是旧 family 的盲目 K 轴细扫，而是在连续两轮正信号后，对当前最有希望的中低成本三段式主线做一次必要的上沿确认。选择 `128` 而不是先改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，是因为当前最清楚的未决问题仍是 lookup budget 斜率是否继续存在；若 r99 已接近饱和，这轮会直接给出答案。主要风险是 FVU 改善很小而成本继续上升，但这同样有价值，因为它会告诉我们后续该把预算转向预算重分配或新 family，而不是继续堆 K。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r98 (`lowrank_expert_residual K=96 TRUNK_RANK=40 NUM_EXPERTS=32`) 到 r99 (`K=112`) 给出连续正斜率，说明当前压缩版三段式结构的收益不只来自 residual 是否存在，也仍受 deployment budget 影响。","当前最有信息量的问题是 `lowrank_expert_residual` 在这套压缩 recipe 下的 K-knee 上沿，而不是继续回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 做局部补点。","按当前 fresh cost 估算，`lowrank_expert_residual K=128 TRUNK_RANK=40 NUM_EXPERTS=32 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算，并处于允许的中低成本结构对照带。","当前不要把 `expert_topk ACTIVE_EXPERTS>1` 的负信号外推到 future shared+routed-expert family；但在现有 family 仍有清晰单变量正斜率时，也不应提前切去 code-edit。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=128` 继续明显优于 r99，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，测试在已确认更高 K 有效后，expert 段与 residual 段的最优预算分配。","如果 `K=128` 只带来极小改善，则说明这条 family 在当前压缩 recipe 下的 deployment knee 已接近 `K=112`；下一轮应停止继续堆 K，转而测试 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或准备 shared+routed-expert 新 family。","如果 `K=128` 意外退化，则说明 r98-r99 的收益更可能来自较低 K 正则化或训练噪声；下一轮应回到 `K=112`，并优先做同 family 的预算重分配验证而不是继续上探。"]}
research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/logs/agent_action_0035.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Ten no-improve rounds indicate the current fixed-per-sample-K search direction is fundamentally flawed, and recent pivots like `jumprelu` and `two_stage_residual` still stayed far behind the frontier. The next coherent architecture move is to change the sparsity mechanism itself: add `adaptive_budget_topk`, which keeps the same overall batch budget but allocates support dynamically across samples based on encoding difficulty instead of enforcing a rigid per-sample K. If hard examples need more active features and easy examples need fewer, this dynamic-budget routing could improve the quality frontier without changing the execution layer.","summary":"Add a new `adaptive_budget_topk` family under `sparsify/` and run a proxy comparison at K=128 with the current strong shared recipe (`EXPANSION_FACTOR=32`, signum, `LR=1.6e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0`). This is a genuine architecture pivot away from fixed per-sample TopK and tests whether dynamic batch-level support allocation is a better search direction than more tuning on the current mainline.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"adaptive_budget_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This round follows the mandatory architecture pivot and changes one core dimension only: the sparse allocation mechanism. The implementation is confined to `sparsify/`, registers cleanly with the existing config factory, and a local forward/backward smoke test passed with visibly non-uniform per-sample active counts under a shared batch budget.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"adaptive_budget_topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"32"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"HOOKPOINTS","value":"layers.[3].self_attn.o_proj"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Added `adaptive_budget_topk`, a new sparse architecture that allocates a fixed batch-level feature budget dynamically across samples instead of enforcing the same K for every sample.","Registered `adaptive_budget_topk` in the existing architecture validation and factory paths under `sparsify/` only.","Local smoke test passed for `adaptive_budget_topk` forward/backward execution, and the encoded supports showed non-uniform per-sample active counts under batch execution."],"next_hypotheses":["If `adaptive_budget_topk` is competitive at K=128 proxy, keep the family alive and promote to full before local tuning.","If quality is promising but runtime is flagged as poor, follow with a narrow performance-oriented `code_fix` on the dynamic-budget path rather than discarding the family immediately.","If `adaptive_budget_topk` remains clearly behind, archive dynamic-budget routing and pivot to a different fundamentally different mechanism rather than returning to lowrank_gated_residual micro-tuning."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0147.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.3e-3"}],"expected_win":"confirm_signal","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 静态库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 静态字典库 {b_i} 都可离线导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r145 表明把 signum 学习率从主线参考值 3.0e-3 小幅上调到 3.3e-3 后，FVU 从 0.058106 降到 0.057939，且总耗时未恶化；r146 的 policy_reject 说明不能把这一步包装成 clean baseline，本轮必须继续作为单变量 LR 问题处理。本轮只回答一个问题：相对于当前主线参考配方的 LR=3.0e-3，把 LR 改为 3.3e-3 的收益是否可重复成立，并且不会以更差的 tokens_per_sec、总耗时或 final_total_tokens 为代价。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 LR=3.3e-3 再次优于 3.0e-3，且运行代价基本不变，则可把 3.3e-3 视为新的 signum 主线锚点，后续再决定是否继续微调或转入 optimizer/成本轴。","若 LR=3.3e-3 回落到 3.0e-3 基线附近，则说明 r145 更可能是噪声收益，后续应关闭上探并保守回到 3.0e-3。","若 LR=3.3e-3 只带来极小收益但显著拖慢训练，则将其视为负面 recipe 信号，不再继续围绕更高 LR 上探。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 仍是当前兼容 frontier 上质量最强的可行主线，导出形式未变，继续属于扩展兼容。","r145 首次在 EF=2/K=128/signum 主线上得到 0.057939，因此当前最有价值的问题是确认这个 LR 信号是否可复现。","r146 的 policy_reject 表明必须把 3.3e-3 继续视为 LR 轴单变量问题，而不是以 clean baseline 名义提交。"],"primary_variable":"lr","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：只改 LR，family、EF、K、optimizer 与导出形式全部固定，不混入成本轴、loss 轴或新的结构变化。这样既符合当前推荐顺序，也避开了 r146 暴露出的 clean-baseline 包装问题。风险是再次运行 3.3e-3 可能只复现到接近 3.0e-3 的结果，因此评估时必须同时看完整曲线、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，而不是只看最终 FVU。","summary":"继续围绕当前主线 family 推进，不开新 family；将 r145 的 3.3e-3 结果当作单变量 LR 信号而非新 baseline，保持 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum 不变，再运行一次 LR=3.3e-3，确认该小幅上调是否能稳定优于参考配方的 3.0e-3。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0229.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"224"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"frontier_mapping","hypothesis":"候选 family: jumprelu。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；JumpReLU 只改变单样本在线侧的阈值化支持形成与系数计算，不改变 decoder 端的单库有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 r228 只改一个 env 参数 `K=224`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=jumprelu`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH=0.05`、`JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD=0.02`、`signum`、`LR=0.003` 不变，测试在 r228 已经于更低部署成本点压过同区间 topk 的前提下，继续缩短查表链路后是否仍能保持明显质量优势，从而把 jumprelu 前沿从约 0.48x 进一步扩展到约 0.47x。该改动只降低 deployment 查表成本，不增加 encoder 成本，预计 total_cost 约从 0.48x 降到 0.47x，仍满足 LUTurbo 总成本硬约束。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `jumprelu@K224` 仍明显优于当前同区间 `topk@K224` 的 FVU=0.15281，且训练时长未恶化，则继续相对本轮单变量下探到 `K=192`，补齐更低部署成本侧的 Pareto 形状。","如果 `K=224` 的 FVU 仅小幅变差但仍优于 topk，且运行代价接近或优于 r228，则可将 jumprelu 视为 `<0.5x` 区域沿 K 轴可稳定外推的直兼容主线。","如果 `K=224` 的 FVU 退化到接近或差于同区间 topk，则停止 jumprelu 的 K 下探线，转向新的低成本 family，而不是继续消耗在这条高 K 依赖支线上。"],"notes_to_memory":["r228 已证明 `jumprelu@K240` 在更低部署成本点仍优于同区间 topk：FVU=0.14756 对比 `topk@K240` 的 0.14833，同时 duration=391s，没有出现比近期 jumprelu 轮更差的系统代价。","当前最高信息量问题是 jumprelu 的质量优势能否继续沿 K 轴向更低 deployment 成本扩展，而不是继续在 `K=240` 单点上做 recipe 微调。","评估本轮时必须同步比较 FVU、tokens_per_sec、duration_sec、final_total_tokens；若质量收益极小但训练明显更慢，应视为负面信号。"],"reference_round":228,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r228 只改 `K`，不联动 architecture、EF、LR、bandwidth、init_threshold 或其他 recipe。选择继续下探到 `K=224`，是因为 r228 已经满足开放假设的前半条件：在更低 deployment 成本处仍压过同区间 topk，且总时长没有恶化；此时继续沿同一成本轴补点，比再次切到高不确定性新 family 更能直接服务于 `<0.5x` Pareto 前沿补全。主要风险是 jumprelu 的改进对极高 K 过于敏感，但这正是本轮要隔离回答的单一问题。","summary":"相对 r228 的 `jumprelu@EF1,K240,JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH=0.05,JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD=0.02` 做一次严格 param_only frontier probe，仅将 `K` 下调到 `224`。目标是在进一步降低总成本的同时，验证 jumprelu 能否继续压过当前 `topk@0.47x` 邻近点，从而把 `<0.5x` 区域更低 deployment 成本侧的 Pareto 前沿补完整。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0068.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`lowrank_soft_codebook_residual` has now improved the frontier at `K=16`, `K=8`, and `K=4`; pushing the same fixed recipe to `K=2` may extend this family into the extreme low-K regime and potentially beat the current `K=2` anchor from `lowrank_residual`.","summary":"Run one controlled parameter-only experiment at `K=2` with `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual`, keeping `EF=12`, `signum`, `LR=3.2e-3`, and `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` fixed so `K` is the only changed variable.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"smaller_k","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This is still the highest-value single-variable move. The family has produced three consecutive frontier improvements as K decreased, so testing `K=2` is more justified than switching families before the current trend breaks.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"2"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 68 tests whether `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual`, now on the frontier at `K=16`, `K=8`, and `K=4`, can extend further into the extreme low-K regime at `K=2` under the same fixed recipe.","Keep architecture and recipe fixed (`EF=12`, `signum`, `LR=3.2e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0`) so `K` is the only changing dimension.","Success criterion is beating the current `K=2` frontier anchor (`lowrank_residual`, FVU `0.16997215151786804`) or establishing another non-dominated low-K point for the family."],"next_hypotheses":["If `K=2` wins, test `K=1` with the same family to see whether the family can cover the full low-K frontier.","If `K=2` is close but slightly behind, consider one confirmatory rerun before concluding the family bottoms out at `K=4`.","If `K=2` clearly loses, keep `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual` as strongest in the `K=4-16` band and resume new-family search for `K<=2`."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0048.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","reference_round":42,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r。也就是先用静态 low-rank trunk 向量库 U={u_r} 重构平滑主干，再对残差用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 B_e={b_{e,i}} 并做局部 sparse 选择；因此它仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。Round 43 的 blocker 不是结构质量，而是运行时观测路径错误：`from sparsify import SparseCoder` 直接实例化时没有尊重 `cfg.architecture`，导致 policy behavioral-diff 实际在比较 topk vs topk，误把 `lowrank_expert_topk` 判成与 topk 完全相同。本轮只修复 `sparsify/` 内的构造分发，使直接构造 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 时也能按 `cfg.architecture` 返回正确 family，然后按 r43 的原设计重跑相对 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的低成本 probe，验证这条 `lowrank + expert` 结构在约 0.44x total_cost 下是否真能形成新的 Pareto 段。","summary":"当前优先级最高的不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 上做第四个低成本邻域点，而是先修掉 Round 43 暴露出的系统 blocker：`lowrank_expert_topk` 被 policy 的 behavioral diff 误拦。修复 `SparseCoder` 的直接构造分发后，按原计划重跑 r43 的 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 低成本验证，可以在不引入新 tunable 的前提下重新回答 `lowrank + expert` 这条高优先级结构线是否值得继续。","self_review":"满足当前阶段的运行时优先级：先修 blocker，再做结构比较。代码改动限制在 `sparsify/`，不碰 evaluation semantics，也不改 AutoResearch/launcher；真正实验配置相对 r42 仍只改一个 env 参数 `TRUNK_RANK=128`。这次 repair 的目标不是改训练语义，而是让公共构造入口与 `cfg.architecture` 一致，避免再次把 policy 误判当成结构结论。风险是修复后 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的真实低成本效果可能仍然一般；但那时才能把它当成结构证据，而不是观测链路伪影。","touched_files":["sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 43 的 `policy_reject` 根因是 exported `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 直接构造时未按 `cfg.architecture` 分发，behavioral diff 实际比较成了 topk vs topk。","`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容，不是动态字典。","按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=192 EF=1 TRUNK_RANK=128` 的 total_cost 约为 0.44x，修复 blocker 后应优先拿到这个点的真实 FVU，再决定该 family 是否继续。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果修复后 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的真实结果在约 0.44x 成本下明显优于当前 `<0.5x` anchor，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=64`，测试 lowrank+expert 是否还能继续向左延伸。","如果修复后该点仍明显弱于 `jumprelu`/`lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本点，则应归档 `lowrank_expert_topk`，把预算转回其他高优先级结构方向。","如果修复后仍有新的 runtime/policy blocker，则下一轮继续只处理新 blocker，不把结果当成架构质量结论。"]}
