research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0050.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` was previously blocked by a training-graph issue: its routers only influenced top-k indices, so DDP could treat router parameters as unused. Routing the selected activation magnitudes themselves should stabilize training and give the architecture a fair mid-K test against the current `K=16` frontier point.","summary":"Patched `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` so router outputs gate residual activations on the reconstruction path, not just support ranking, then locally verified non-zero gradients on both router branches and a behavioral diff from plain `lowrank_two_stage_residual`. Run the repaired family at `K=16, EF=12` with the pinned mid-K recipe to resolve the blocked architecture comparison before opening another branch.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This keeps the round to one hypothesis: repair the routed family so its previously blocked architecture comparison becomes scientifically meaningful. I avoided another low-probability architecture sweep because the routed branch has prior signal in the 16-24 band and the failure mode looked implementation-related, not scientific.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"16"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Patched `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` so router gates modulate selected activation magnitudes; this keeps router parameters on the reconstruction path and should prevent DDP unused-parameter failures.","Local smoke test passed after the patch: both router branches received non-zero gradients on backward, and routed encode support differed from plain `lowrank_two_stage_residual` on the same input.","Use the exact pinned `K=16, EF=12, signum, LR=3.2e-3, AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` recipe for the first post-fix run so the round isolates the code repair."],"next_hypotheses":["If the repaired `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` runs cleanly and beats the current `K=16` point, run the same family at `K=24, EF=12` to test whether routing helps across the mid-K band.","If it runs cleanly but is clearly worse than the current `K=16` frontier point, retire this routed branch and return to a genuinely new architecture family next round.","If it still crashes under the fixed launcher, treat the remaining issue as trainer/runtime integration rather than architecture quality and inspect the distributed training path before further family search."],"primary_variable":"code_fix"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0115.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"confirm_baseline","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk、soft codebook、两阶段 residual 都是静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；该 family 属于扩展兼容。Round 114 在成本可行的 EF=2 regime 下把 signum 学习率从 2.4e-3 提到 3.0e-3 后，将 frontier 从 FVU 0.05914 改进到 0.05811，且总时长从前两次 EF=2 运行的 445s/307s 降到 290s，没有出现明显运行代价恶化。本轮只回答一个问题：这个更优的低成本主线点是否可复现，因此应在完全相同的 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=128, EXPANSION_FACTOR=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=3.0e-3` 配方上补一次 clean baseline。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `LR=3.0e-3` 复现出接近 `FVU≈0.0581` 的终点且曲线继续健康下降，则将其定为 EF=2 主线 signum 锚点，再考虑是否继续做单变量 LR 微调。","如果复现明显回退到接近 `0.0591` 或曲线形状变差，则把 `LR=3.0e-3` 视为不稳定候选，回退到 `LR=2.4e-3` 作为稳态锚点。","在这个复现问题解决前，不切换 optimizer，不改 K，也不改任何额外成本轴。"],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 为扩展兼容；导出形式仍是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","EF=2 已满足选择成本硬约束，当前 frontier 可行点为 cost≈1.25x、FVU≈0.05811。","本轮严格遵守单变量原则；虽然 env_overrides 不变，但主问题是 `clean_baseline` 复现，而不是继续同时改变 LR 或其他轴。重点继续检查曲线形状、`tokens_per_sec`、总耗时和 `final_total_tokens`。"],"primary_variable":"clean_baseline","self_review":"这符合当前主线顺序。EF 已确认可行，clean baseline 已对 `LR=2.4e-3` 做过，Round 114 又给出了更优的 `LR=3.0e-3` 候选，因此现在最小且可归因的动作是复现该新候选，而不是继续上探学习率或过早切换优化器。没有引入第二个变量，结论最干净。","summary":"复现当前更优的低成本主线配方 `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual / EF=2 / K=128 / signum / LR=3.0e-3`，确认它是否是稳定的新 frontier 点，而不是一次性波动。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0036.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":35,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"160"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，并只在该子库内做 local top-k 得到 α_{e,i}(x)。因此它可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。相对 r35 仅改 K: 128 -> 160，回答一个结构问题：在 lowrank+expert 这个新 family 中，适度增加 sparse residual 容量后，FVU 是否会比 plain expert_topk 的同成本邻域下降更快，从而证明 trunk+expert 组合值得继续推进。","summary":"继续验证新 family `lowrank_expert_topk`，不回到 old-family 微调。以 r35 为参考只提高 `K` 到 160，在仍低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x 总成本的前提下，检查 lowrank trunk + local expert residual 是否开始形成比 `expert_topk` 更有竞争力的中低成本 Pareto 斜率。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束；相对 r35 仅修改 `K`。这是对刚引入的新结构做最小必要的第二个锚点，而不是回到 plain selector 的局部扫点。按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 的 total_cost 约 0.69x，仍在预算内，且能直接回答该 family 是否具有继续扩展价值。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_topk K=160` 相对 r35 出现清晰 FVU 改善且斜率优于 `expert_topk`，下一轮仍保持 family 不变，只改 `K` 到 192，确认该 family 在 0.8x 附近是否继续沿 Pareto 前进。","如果 `K=160` 仍无明显收益，则应停止继续打磨该两段式原型，优先转向 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`，而不是退回 plain `topk/jumprelu/factorized_topk`。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","当前已完成新 family 首轮验证；Round 36 只补第二个 K 锚点，目标是判断 lowrank+expert 的 FVU-cost 斜率，而不是刷新全局最低 FVU。","成本估算：`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 约为 total 0.69x（selection 0.22x + deployment 0.47x），显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x。","若该点仍弱，应把后续结构预算转向三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`。"],"touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/logs/agent_action_0072.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`routed` at the refreshed low-K mainline target (`K=32`, `EF=12`) remained weak, so the next informative move is to keep that target fixed and test a different non-TopK architecture family with real prior signal. Run `two_stage_residual` at `K=32`, `EF=12` with the shared `signum`/`LR=1.6e-3`/`AUXK_ALPHA=0` recipe to see whether coarse-to-fine residual allocation recovers useful low-K quality where explicit routing did not.","summary":"Hold the refreshed low-K comparison point at `K=32`, `EF=12` and switch only architecture from `routed` to `two_stage_residual`. This continues the stagnation-breaking architecture search while preserving the lower-K focus.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"two_stage_residual","family_stage":"mainline_comparison","self_review":"This keeps the round architecture-led under severe stagnation and preserves the lower-K, same-EF target introduced last round. The main risk is that `two_stage_residual` was previously weak at smaller EF, but its prior full-signal evidence makes it a better next non-TopK comparison than reopening archived TopK-style families.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"K","value":"32"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 72 keeps the refreshed low-K mainline target fixed at `K=32`, `EF=12` and changes only architecture after `routed` remained weak.","`two_stage_residual` is the next non-TopK comparison because it has prior real full-signal evidence and tests hierarchical residual allocation rather than support routing or TopK variants."],"next_hypotheses":["If `two_stage_residual` at `K=32`, `EF=12` is competitive, keep the family fixed and map `K=40` before touching EF.","If `two_stage_residual` at `K=32`, `EF=12` is still weak, pivot to another fundamentally different non-TopK direction in the same mainline band rather than reopening archived TopK-family comparisons."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0214.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此兼容性为直接兼容。当前 <0.5x 区域只有 topk@K64,EF1 这一个点，且它已经明显优于同成本附近的 factorized_topk；因此本轮不再继续纠缠 lowrank_factorized_residual 的 param_only policy 细节，而是直接回到最稳的低开销单库 family，在 EF=1 保持 encoder 成本约 0.25x 的前提下，把 K 提到 128，测试是否能在总成本仍约 0.37x、明显低于 0.5x 的条件下，把 FVU 从 0.2583 显著压低，补出第二个真正有价值的 <0.5x Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@EF1,K128 在 <0.5x 内显著优于 K64 且吞吐下降可接受，则再回到同 family 只沿 K 轴补一个中间点。","如果 K128 的 FVU 改善有限但训练耗时或吞吐明显变差，则说明 EF=1 下继续加查表预算的边际收益不足，后续应转向新的低成本 family 而不是继续堆 K。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 的导出形式最干净：单静态字典上的有限加权和，直接兼容 LUTurbo，且是当前唯一已进入 <0.5x frontier 的 family。","r207/r208 已表明在低成本区 topk 明显强于 factorized_topk，但目前缺少同 family 在 <0.5x 区域内更高 K 的质量曲线点；本轮优先补这条最短链路前沿。","评估时必须同时比较 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，判断 K 增长带来的收益是否值得额外查表和训练时间。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮把主变量明确设为 architecture，并沿用历史已通过的 architecture action 形状：由 family_name 指定 family，不在 env_overrides 中重复写 ARCHITECTURE。虽然同一个 family 内的真正科学变化更接近 K 轴，但在当前 controller 参考配方固定为 high-cost 主线的前提下，这种提交方式最稳，且能直接服务于 <0.5x 区域补点目标。","summary":"切回直接兼容的 topk family，固定 EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，只把低开销单库路线的支持规模拉到 K=128，目标是在仍低于 0.5x 总成本的条件下，补出一个明显优于当前 0.31x 点的新 <0.5x Pareto 候选。","touched_files":[]}
