research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0007.json:27:    "env_overrides": [
research/history/logs/agent_action_0008.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"继续使用直接兼容 family `topk`，最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i in S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时，`{b_i}` 仍是单个静态向量库；在线流程仍是 top-k 选择、系数计算、查表 `W b_i`、加权求和，并可保留选择性补偿接口。本轮相对 r1 仅将训练优化器从 `signum` 改为 `adam`，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=topk, K=64, EXPANSION_FACTOR=1, LR=8e-4` 不变的同一成本与结构槽位下，检查当前主线是否受优化器形态限制而未能把训练曲线压低。","summary":"兼容性判断：`topk` 为直接兼容。Round 7 已经表明简单下调 `LR` 不能改善当前主线，因此继续只在 signum 内微调学习率的信息增量开始下降；但本轮策略仍要求先把同一 family 的 recipe 看清，所以最合适的单变量问题是优化器本身。将 `OPTIMIZER` 从 `signum` 切到 `adam` 不改变 total_cost，仍约为 `0.31x`，但能直接回答当前 `topk@K=64,EF=1` 的 FVU 是否主要受优化动态而非结构限制。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"遵守单变量原则，基于 `reference_round=1` 仅修改 `OPTIMIZER`。这轮归因清晰：结构、成本带、K、EF 都不变，只检验优化器是否能改善收敛。如果 `adam` 仍不能优于 `signum`，则当前 `topk` 主线 recipe 基本可视为摸清，下一轮应更积极转向新结构或高优先级未验证方向。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`topk@K=64,EF=1` 仍是当前 `<0.5x` 区域最佳主线点；Round 8 用优化器切换而非继续调学习率。","`OPTIMIZER` 切换不改变 LUTurbo cost proxy，可直接用于区分是训练动力学问题还是结构上限问题。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `adam` 优于 `signum`，下一轮可围绕 `topk@K=64` 继续做小幅 recipe 校准。","如果 `adam` 仍无改善，则应停止继续打磨当前 `topk` recipe，转向新的兼容结构族或开始轻量 expert 子库方向的最小实现。"],"reference_round":1}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0005.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Keeping `lowrank_two_stage_residual` fixed and dropping only `K` from 8 to 4 will test whether this family can still add a non-dominated ultra-low-K point, completing the current low-K sweep before changing architecture.","summary":"Continue the controlled same-family sweep with a parameter-only run at `K=4`, while pinning the established recipe (`ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_residual`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0`). The `K=8` result remained keep-worthy, so the next most informative move is to finish tracing the low-K tail on the same family.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"smaller_k","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This preserves variable isolation, extends the existing Pareto mapping cleanly, and avoids switching families before the current low-K lane is fully characterized.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"4"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 5 extends the controlled `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K sweep from 8 to 4 with all other recipe fields pinned.","The family has produced keep-worthy points at K=32, 24, 16, and 8, so finishing the ultra-low-K tail is more informative than switching architectures immediately."],"next_hypotheses":["If `K=4` stays competitive, continue to `K=2` on the same family to see where this architecture stops being Pareto-relevant.","If `K=4` degrades too sharply, shift back to the 16-24 regime and test a routed variant for better support allocation.","If `K=4` is borderline but interesting, keep the family fixed and tune stage allocation rather than changing the broader recipe."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/logs/agent_action_0008.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`two_stage_residual` has now produced a real full-fidelity gain at K=128, so the next informative move is to map whether that architectural win also strengthens the lower-K Pareto frontier rather than assuming the gain is confined to the anchor point. Running the same strong recipe at K=64 isolates whether staged residual allocation preserves enough of the new quality advantage to create a better non-dominated tradeoff than the current gated K=64 point.","summary":"Run a `two_stage_residual` proxy comparison at K=64 using the same signum/EF=16/aux-free recipe that just improved the K=128 full frontier, changing only K.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"pareto_improve","family_name":"two_stage_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This keeps the search on the newly validated winning family and changes only K, which is the cleanest way to test whether the new architecture improves the broader Pareto frontier rather than only the K=128 anchor. Risk: the staged residual design may rely on higher budget and degrade sharply at K=64, but that is exactly the missing frontier information.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 7 established `two_stage_residual` as the new K=128 full frontier leader with FVU 0.13607123959809542, materially beating gated.","This round tests whether the same architecture also improves the lower-K Pareto frontier by changing only K from 128 to 64 under the winning recipe."],"next_hypotheses":["If `two_stage_residual` at K=64 beats the current gated K=64 frontier point, keep extending the family down the K axis, including K=32.","If K=64 regresses sharply, keep K=128 as the mainline anchor and stabilize family-specific internals rather than abandoning the architecture.","If K=64 is quality-competitive but runtime is poor, follow with a performance-focused implementation pass instead of treating it as an architectural miss."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0050.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","reference_round":42,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r。也就是先用静态 low-rank trunk 向量库 U={u_r} 重构平滑主干，再对残差用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 B_e={b_{e,i}} 并做局部 sparse 选择；因此它仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。Round 48 和 Round 49 都表明 blocker 仍然是运行时构造路径，而不是结构质量：policy behavioral diff 通过 `from sparsify import SparseCoder` 直接实例化时，`cfg.architecture=lowrank_expert_topk` 仍未生效，比较结果依旧变成 topk vs topk。本轮主任务是继续修复 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` 中的直接构造分发，让 `SparseCoder(1024, SparseCoderConfig(architecture='lowrank_expert_topk', ...))` 真正返回对应 family，然后按 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的原计划重跑，拿到这条 `lowrank + expert` 结构在约 0.44x total_cost 下的首个有效点。","summary":"当前最高优先级仍是消除重复 blocker，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 上打磨低成本邻域点。r48、r49 连续两轮都显示 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在 behavioral diff 阶段被误拦，且 round summary 里 `touched_files=[]`、`patch_path=null`，说明修复并未真正落地；因此 Round 50 应继续做最小 repair，把 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 的分发修通，再重跑相对 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的低成本 probe。","self_review":"满足当前阶段的运行时优先级：先消除 blocker，再做结构比较。代码改动范围仍只限 `sparsify/`，不改 evaluation semantics，也不改 AutoResearch/launcher；实验配置相对 r42 仍只改一个 env 参数 `TRUNK_RANK=128`。这次 repair 需要给出可验证的完成标准：1. 直接构造 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 时按 `cfg.architecture` 分发；2. 用完全相同的 `architecture=lowrank_expert_topk, K=192, EF=1` 做 instantiate/forward/backward smoke；3. behavioral diff 不再把它判成 topk。风险是修复后该 family 的真实效果可能仍不强；但那时才是有效结构结论，而不是观测链路伪影。","touched_files":["sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["r48 和 r49 之后可以确认：当前 blocker 仍是 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 直接构造路径没有正确尊重 `cfg.architecture`，而不是 `lowrank_expert_topk` 本身的结构质量。","`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是静态 trunk 库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。","按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=192 EF=1 TRUNK_RANK=128` 的 total_cost 约为 0.44x；修复 blocker 后应优先获得这个点的真实 FVU。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 repair 后 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的真实结果在约 0.44x 成本下明显优于当前 `<0.5x` anchor，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=64`，测试 lowrank+expert 是否还能继续向左延伸。","如果 repair 后该点仍明显弱于 `jumprelu` 或 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本点，则应归档 `lowrank_expert_topk`，把预算转回其他高优先级结构方向。","如果 repair 后出现新的失败模式，则下一轮继续只处理新的 blocker，不把结果误判为架构质量结论。"]}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0139.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"After three distinct K32 soft-codebook backbones failed to beat the bucketed point under `EF=16`, the next severe-stagnation step should continue architecture search only along an already-registered but mechanistically different branch rather than return to scalar tweaks. `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual` is the strongest remaining soft-codebook variant by prior results and may yield a better small-K tradeoff at `K=32, EF=16` by using learned gating instead of bucket partitioning or hard routing.","summary":"Run an architecture-only comparison at `K=32, EF=16` with `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual`, keeping `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=3.2e-3`, and `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` fixed. This follows the severe-stagnation policy to stop minor tweaks and test a fundamentally different existing architecture on the most valuable exposed small-K slot.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This is a policy-clean architecture-only move: same K, same EF, same optimizer recipe, only the backbone changes. I chose the gated soft-codebook branch because it has a stronger prior than other untried alternatives in this regime and offers a real structural contrast to the bucketed, plain two-stage, and routed variants already tested.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"32"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 139 continues severe-stagnation recovery by testing `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual` at the same `K=32, EF=16` target after plain and routed soft-codebook variants both failed to beat the bucketed baseline.","Keep the recipe pinned to `signum`, `LR=3.2e-3`, and `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` so the result isolates architecture alone.","This run asks whether learned gating is a better capacity-allocation mechanism than bucketing or routing for the current small-K EF=16 frontier slot."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual` improves the `K=32, EF=16` point, propagate it to `K=64` before returning to recipe tuning.","If it is close but slightly worse at `K=32`, consider one preprocessing or optimizer probe on this gated backbone rather than discarding it immediately.","If it clearly loses at `K=32`, treat the soft-codebook family search as largely exhausted under the current recipe and pivot to under-explored runtime axes on the existing bucketed backbone."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0005.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"切到直接兼容 family `jumprelu`，最终重构公式仍为 `x_hat = Σ_{i in S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时，`{b_i}` 仍是单个静态向量库；在线链路仍是先形成支持集 `S(x)`、再计算系数、查表 `W b_i`、加权求和，阈值门控只改变支持形成方式，不改变静态库导出形式。本轮相对 r1 仅修改 `ARCHITECTURE`，在保持 `K=64, EXPANSION_FACTOR=1` 不变的同成本槽位下，测试 JumpReLU 的阈值化支持选择能否优于 plain top-k。","summary":"兼容性判断：`jumprelu` 为直接兼容。`factorized_topk` 在同成本带已经给出负结果，继续围绕它微调信息增量不高；下一步最干净的是换到另一个同成本、同部署开销、但支持形成机制不同的直接兼容 family。按当前本地成本估计，`jumprelu@K=64,EF=1` 的 total_cost 仍约 `0.31x`（selection `0.25x` + deployment `0.06x`），与当前最佳 `topk@K=64` 完全同槽位，适合做 matched architecture probe。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"遵守单变量原则，基于 `reference_round=1` 仅修改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮回答的问题很单一：在不改变 cost band、不引入额外部署复杂度的前提下，阈值化支持形成是否比 plain top-k 更适合当前 hookpoint。若仍无改进，说明当前 low-cost 区的直接兼容单库 family 已经出现连续负信号，后续应更积极转向其他结构槽位或高优先级未验证方向。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"jumprelu"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`jumprelu` 直接兼容 LUTurbo：最终形式仍是单静态向量库上的有限加权和 `Σ α_i b_i`，阈值只影响支持形成。","本地成本估计显示 `jumprelu@K=64,EF=1` 与 `topk@K=64,EF=1` 同为约 `0.31x` total_cost，适合做 matched probe。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `jumprelu@64` 优于 `topk@64`，下一轮可在该 family 内做 `K` 邻域或带宽相关探索。","如果 `jumprelu@64` 仍不优于 `topk@64`，下一轮应优先切到新的结构槽位，例如 `whitened_topk` 的更高但仍 `<0.5x` 成本带，或开始准备轻量 expert 子库方向的最小实现。"],"reference_round":1}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0139.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_perf_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(x-x_stage1)} γ_m(x) c_m，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是 shared 静态向量库，{B_e} 是 routed expert 静态子库，C={c_m} 是全局 residual 静态库，x_stage1 为 shared+routed stage 的重构。在线导出链路仍是“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + 单 expert local top-k + residual library lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r138 仅把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`、`K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，利用 residual cleanup 吃掉少掉的第二个 routed expert 覆盖，从而把 total_cost 从约 0.60x 压到约 0.52x，同时尽量保住 r138 的 FVU=0.0946，回答这条 hetero MoE + residual 线能否在 0.5x 左右形成新的结构性 Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 仍接近 r138 的 FVU，则下一轮保持该 family 不变，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 或 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 继续向 <0.5x 压缩。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 明显掉点，则说明这条线当前仍依赖双 expert 覆盖，下一轮优先回到 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 做 matched-cost 容量压缩，而不是继续削 router path。","若训练前 override 校验再次失败，应先检查 family-specific allowlist 是否被 runtime 热加载到最新代码，而不要把失败误判成架构结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 的 AutoResearch override allowlist，真实改动仅在 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`。","本地校验通过：`validate_env_overrides(..., fallback_architecture='shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual')` 现在接受 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`、`STAGE1_RATIO`，同时仍拒绝未消费的 `TRUNK_RANK`。","成本自检：在 r138 配方下把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 设为 1 后，selection_accesses=1646592、deployment_accesses=524288、combined_accesses=2170880，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.52，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":138,"self_review":"先修真实 blocker，再发实验：r138 已证明 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 有结构价值，但此前它没有接入 family-specific override allowlist，后续任何合法的单变量 param-only 探针都会在训练前被判为 disallowed。当前已实际补上该 wiring，并做了本地 allowlist 自检。计划运行时相对 r138 只改 1 个 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，满足单变量原则；风险是第二个 routed expert 仍对当前 target 很关键，导致 FVU 回退，但这会直接回答 residual stage 是否足以支撑更轻的 expert 激活路径。","summary":"已实际修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 的参数接线 blocker，使该新 family 后续可以合法做单变量 param-only 探针。建议本轮以 r138 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，直接测试“shared low-rank basis + 单 routed expert + residual cleanup”能否把这条 hetero MoE 线从约 0.60x 压到约 0.52x total_cost，并保持足够接近 r138 的质量。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/logs/agent_action_0007.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Recent alternative families remain well behind gated at K=128, so the next informative move is a genuinely different encoder structure rather than another local sweep. A new `two_stage_residual` SAE that allocates the same total K across a coarse sparse pass and a residual sparse pass may recover more variance at fixed sparsity by turning single-shot TopK selection into staged residual reconstruction.","summary":"Add a `two_stage_residual` prototype under `sparsify/` and run a proxy comparison at K=128 using the current best signum/EF=16/aux-free recipe, changing only architecture.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"two_stage_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This keeps one primary variable isolated at the architecture level and responds to the continued stagnation with a new family instead of another minor tweak. Risk: a first staged-residual prototype may not beat the frontier immediately and could introduce a sanity bug, but proxy plus a narrow code change is the correct scope for this round.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["After `jumprelu`, `lowrank_residual`, and `whitened_topk` all trailed badly at K=128 proxy, this round pivots to a new staged-residual architecture rather than more single-pass tuning.","`two_stage_residual` tests whether hierarchical sparse allocation at fixed total K can outperform one-shot support selection on the current activation space."],"next_hypotheses":["If `two_stage_residual` shows a clear proxy gain over recent non-gated families, keep incubating it with a family-specific split-of-K stabilization pass before any full request.","If the prototype is competitive but slow, follow with an `edit_perf_code` round instead of discarding the family on architectural grounds.","If the prototype is clearly uncompetitive, pivot again to another fundamentally different mechanism such as a softer or batch-level sparsity architecture rather than returning to gated-local tweaks."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0049.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","reference_round":42,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r。也就是先用静态 low-rank trunk 向量库 U={u_r} 重构平滑主干，再对残差用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 B_e={b_{e,i}} 并做局部 sparse 选择；因此它仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。r48 已明确表明当前 blocker 仍然是运行时构造路径：policy behavioral diff 通过 `from sparsify import SparseCoder` 直接实例化时，`cfg.architecture=lowrank_expert_topk` 仍未生效，导致比较结果依旧变成 topk vs topk。本轮主任务是继续修复 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` 中的直接构造分发，让 `SparseCoder(1024, SparseCoderConfig(architecture='lowrank_expert_topk', ...))` 真正返回对应 family，然后按 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的原计划重跑，拿到这条 `lowrank + expert` 结构在约 0.44x total_cost 下的首个有效点。","summary":"Round 48 证明 blocker 还没有消除：`lowrank_expert_topk` 再次在 behavioral diff 阶段被误拦，而且这次 round summary 显示并没有真正落地代码补丁。当前优先级最高的是继续做最小 repair，而不是回到 `lowrank_expert_residual` 再打磨一个低成本邻域点；先把 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 的分发修通，再重跑相对 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的低成本 probe，才能把 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的成败当成结构证据。","self_review":"满足当前阶段的运行时优先级：先消除重复 blocker，再做架构比较。代码改动范围仍只限 `sparsify/`，不改 evaluation semantics，也不改 AutoResearch/launcher；实验配置相对 r42 仍只改一个 env 参数 `TRUNK_RANK=128`。这次 repair 需要按架构集成 checklist 做完整验证：修复直接构造分发、用完全相同的 `architecture=lowrank_expert_topk, K=192, EF=1` 做 instantiate/forward/backward smoke，并确认 behavioral diff 不再把它判成 topk。风险是修复后该 family 的真实效果可能仍不强；但那时才是有效结构结论。","touched_files":["sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["r48 之后可以确认：当前 blocker 仍是 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 直接构造路径没有正确尊重 `cfg.architecture`，而不是 `lowrank_expert_topk` 本身的结构质量。","`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是静态 trunk 库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。","按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=192 EF=1 TRUNK_RANK=128` 的 total_cost 约为 0.44x；修复 blocker 后应优先获得这个点的真实 FVU。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 repair 后 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的真实结果在约 0.44x 成本下明显优于当前 `<0.5x` anchor，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=64`，测试 lowrank+expert 是否还能继续向左延伸。","如果 repair 后该点仍明显弱于 `jumprelu` 或 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本点，则应归档 `lowrank_expert_topk`，把预算转回其他高优先级结构方向。","如果 repair 后出现新的失败模式，则下一轮继续只处理新的 blocker，不把结果误判为架构质量结论。"]}
