research/history/logs/agent_action_0061.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判断为扩展兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r60 仅把 ARCHITECTURE 从 `lowrank_expert_topk` 切到 `lowrank_expert_residual`，在保持 `TRUNK_RANK=64`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`K=128`、`EF=1` 不变时，直接回答当前 shared+expert 主干在当前 target 上是否仍明显缺少全局 residual cleanup；如果 r60 的剩余误差主要来自未被 routed expert 覆盖的全局残差结构，则三段式结构应在约 0.7x total_cost 的中成本带把 FVU 显著压低，并形成新的结构性 Pareto 段。","summary":"不回到 plain selector，也不继续做 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的局部 K/LR 微调；以 r60 为 matched reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，验证在已增强的 trunk+expert 主干上，global residual cleanup 是否仍然必要。按当前代码成本估算，这个 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 点约为 encoder 0.54x、deployment 0.19x、total 0.73x，仍明显低于 1.5x 硬预算，属于允许保留的中成本质量锚点。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r60 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。该 family 属于 LUTurbo 扩展兼容 family，不触碰不兼容方向，也不需要新增 tunable 参数接线。之所以优先做这轮 matched 结构切换，而不是继续扫 `TRUNK_RANK` 或 `NUM_EXPERTS`，是因为 r60 已经证明更宽 trunk 的 `lowrank + expert` 在低成本带有效，当前更高信息量的问题变成“ residual cleanup 现在是否仍是主要增益来源”。主要风险是成本会从低成本带抬到中成本带；若 FVU 改善不明显，则说明当前更强的 shared+expert 主干已吃掉大部分可学结构，后续不应继续让三段式局部打磨主导预算。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_residual"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 的 LUTurbo 形式保持为 trunk 静态库 + expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，兼容性为扩展兼容。","Round 61 是对 r60 的 matched 结构对照：同样的 `TRUNK_RANK=64` 与 `NUM_EXPERTS=32` 下，只看加入 residual cleanup 是否带来足够大的质量收益。","按当前代码成本估算，`lowrank_expert_residual K=128 TRUNK_RANK=64 NUM_EXPERTS=32` 约 total_cost 0.73x，远低于 1.5x 硬预算，可作为中成本结构锚点。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 显著优于 r60，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=160` 或回调 `TRUNK_RANK=32`，判断三段式结构的更优 Pareto 落点是在 residual 预算还是 trunk 预算。","如果它只小幅优于 r60，则说明当前 target 上更强的 `lowrank + expert` 已基本足够，后续应优先继续压 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的成本而不是让 residual family 重新主导搜索。","如果结果异常，先核对 round config 与 checkpoint config 中 `architecture=lowrank_expert_residual` 是否真实生效，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"],"reference_round":60}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0013.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"JumpReLU at K=128 may still be under-updating relative to its new 1.6e-3 optimum, and increasing the signum learning rate to 3.2e-3 could further reduce FVU beyond the current 0.1724 full frontier.","summary":"Keep the improved JumpReLU K=128 anchor fixed and continue the LR sweep upward to 3.2e-3 as the next single-parameter refinement.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"quality","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This follows directly from the successful 1.6e-3 promotion and keeps the round tightly scoped to LR only. The main risk is overshooting and degrading training, but the last result justifies testing the next higher bracket before moving to auxk or expansion sweeps.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"jumprelu"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"8"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD","value":"0.15"},{"key":"JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH","value":"0.1"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["LR=1.6e-3 established a new K=128 full frontier for JumpReLU, confirming that optimization rather than architecture was limiting the previous baseline.","Round 13 continues the same K=128 JumpReLU LR sweep by testing 3.2e-3 as the next higher bracket.","This round is intended to check whether the LR improvement trend extends upward or whether 1.6e-3 is already near the useful limit."],"next_hypotheses":["If LR=3.2e-3 improves proxy FVU, promote to full and continue local LR refinement around the new optimum.","If LR=3.2e-3 is worse than 1.6e-3, treat 1.6e-3 as the current LR anchor and begin auxk_alpha sweeps at K=128, starting with 0.","If LR=3.2e-3 is unstable rather than merely worse, stop upward LR exploration and shift to auxk_alpha or expansion-factor sweeps on the 1.6e-3 baseline."],"primary_variable":"lr"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0167.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` with `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=2`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` fixed. Final reconstruction formula is `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m π_m c_m + Σ_i α_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j α_j^(2) b_j`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk library, `{c_m}` is a static soft codebook library, and `{b_i}` is a static residual dictionary; only the stage budget split differs from the mainline. This is `扩展兼容` because LUTurbo can export it as trunk lookup + codebook lookup + two sparse residual lookups over fixed libraries. The single question is whether front-loading the sparse budget is intrinsically worthwhile in the low-EF deployable regime, after keeping the whole matched recipe identical.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["If this asymmetric probe is clearly worse in FVU and runtime metrics, close the family and return to the `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` mainline next round.","If it is similar in FVU with comparable or better throughput, the next single-variable follow-up is `STAGE1_RATIO` tuning within this family rather than opening another new architecture.","If runtime degrades without clear quality gain, treat the extra asymmetry as negative signal even if final FVU is close."],"notes_to_memory":["Compatibility: `扩展兼容`. Export formula is `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m π_m c_m + Σ_i α_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j α_j^(2) b_j`, so each branch maps to static LUTurbo vector libraries.","This round must pin `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=2`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` explicitly; the last three policy rejects were caused by unpinned matched-recipe fields being interpreted as extra variable changes.","Use this probe only to judge architecture worthiness. Check `tokens_per_sec`, total duration, and `final_total_tokens` alongside FVU to see whether any difference comes from better structure or simply slower training."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"This obeys the single-variable rule by changing only `architecture` while explicitly pinning the current mainline recipe fields that previously caused policy rejection. It is the highest-value remaining matched probe because the other feasible low-EF compatible families already have actual EF=2 results, whereas this asymmetric variant has not yet received a valid run. Risk: historical high-EF evidence for asymmetric staging was weak, so this may simply confirm that fixed front-loading is not worth continuing.","summary":"Run one valid matched architecture probe on `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` with the mainline `K=128`, `EF=2`, `signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` recipe explicitly pinned. This cleanly answers whether asymmetric stage allocation is worth any further attention in the current LUTurbo-compatible low-EF regime.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0239.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"48"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"frontier_mapping","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，部署侧仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 reference_round=r238 只改一个 env 参数 `K=48`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=topk`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=signum`、`LR=0.003`、`AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125` 及其余配置不变，测试在约 0.30x 总成本处，是否能把刚建立的左端点 `topk@K32` 的 FVU=0.3199 继续明显压低，并补出 `0.28x -> 0.31x` 之间缺失的 Pareto 过渡点。选择这一步而不是继续开新 family，是因为 r238 已证明最简单单库结构在超低 K 左端优于 `factorized_topk@0.30x`，当前最高信息量问题变成 topk 左侧前沿的真实斜率，而不是再次切到最近已给出负信号的 `codebook_topk`、`factorized_topk` 或 recipe 微调线。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `topk@EF1,K48` 在约 0.30x 成本处显著优于 `K32`，且 `tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens` 没有明显恶化，则相对本轮继续单变量上探到 `K=56` 或直接回接 `K=64`，把左侧低成本前沿补完整。","如果 `K48` 相比 `K32` 改善很小，则说明 `<0.3x` 左端的单库 topk 已接近明显退化区，后续主注意力应回到更高价值的 `0.31x-0.49x` 区间。","如果质量改善存在但运行显著更慢，则按运行时优先级将其记为负面系统信号，不把该配方升格为左侧前沿点。"],"notes_to_memory":["r238 已确认 `topk@EF1,K32` 在约 0.28x 成本处优于当前最左端 `factorized_topk@0.30x`，说明左侧超低成本前沿应由 plain topk 而不是 factorized scorer 主导。","当前 `<0.5x` 前沿在 `0.28x` 与 `0.31x` 之间仍有空档；相对 r238 只提升 `K` 是最小、最可解释、最有利于刻画左端 Pareto 斜率的动作。","评估本轮必须同时比较 `val_fvu`、`tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens`；若只是小幅质量改善但运行明显更慢，应直接视为负面信号。"],"reference_round":238,"self_review":"该提案严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r238 只改 `K`，不联动 architecture、EF、LR、optimizer、AUXK_ALPHA 或任何新参数。主要风险是 `K32->48` 的收益可能不足以形成新的非支配点；但在左端低成本区刚出现正信号后，先补中间过渡点比贸然切回已被证伪的 family 更符合当前 Pareto 补全目标。","summary":"相对 r238 的 `topk@EF1,K32` 做一次严格 param_only 左端补点，仅设置 `K=48`，验证 plain topk 能否在约 0.30x 总成本处继续压低 FVU，并补完整个超低成本左侧前沿。","touched_files":[]}
