research/history_archive/06_20260320_183226/logs/agent_action_0005.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`factorized_topk` missed badly at K=128, so the next plausible quality-focused family is a softly routed multi-expert encoder; `mixture_topk` may improve reconstruction by adding conditional encoder capacity without the hard routing bottlenecks of grouped variants.","summary":"Run a proxy `mixture_topk` experiment at K=128 with the same Adam/LR settings as the current TopK anchor to test whether soft expert routing can materially beat the current 0.211975 full-baseline trajectory.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"mixture_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This is another first-pass architecture probe, so it may still be far from competitive or may need family-specific tuning before it shows value. If it is only slightly better than `factorized_topk` but still far behind TopK, that is not enough to justify promotion.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"mixture_topk"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"3e-4"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`factorized_topk` prototype quality was poor at K=128 proxy (FVU 0.6381136849522591) despite normal runtime, so simple nonlinear hidden mixing does not currently look like a path to the aggressive target.","Keep architecture exploration focused on families with qualitatively different encoder behavior rather than continuing local retuning of the weak `factorized_topk` prototype."],"next_hypotheses":["If `mixture_topk` shows a clear proxy quality gain over plain TopK at K=128, promote it and then tune family-specific capacity.","If `mixture_topk` is also clearly worse than TopK, shift the next architecture probe toward a different sparse activation family such as `jumprelu` or a new routed/multi-branch design.","If `mixture_topk` is promising but slow, follow with a targeted performance pass instead of discarding the family immediately."]}
