research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/round_summaries/round_0076.json:76:      "For launcher compatibility, avoid nonessential override keys like family metadata in `env_overrides`; keep only known training/config parameters.",
research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/round_summaries/round_0076.json:82:      "If the rerun still fails before training, treat it as a narrow compatibility blocker and follow with one repair-focused round rather than judging the family on quality."
