research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0031.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"After five rounds without improvement and with the low-K lane already mapped across `K in {1,2,4,8,16,24,32}`, the next step should be a fundamentally different architecture rather than another minor tweak. `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` may outperform the current `lowrank_two_stage_residual` baseline in the mid-low-K regime when tested as a clean architecture-only swap at `K=16` under the settled recipe.","summary":"Run a pure architecture comparison at `K=16, EF=12` by switching from `lowrank_two_stage_residual` to `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` while keeping optimizer, learning rate, and aux fixed to the current best-controlled low-K recipe.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"fvu","family_name":"routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual","family_stage":"incubating","self_review":"This follows the severe-stagnation policy directly: K coverage is already broad, so the next move must be a fundamentally different architecture. `K=16` is the cleanest comparison point because the routed family was previously identified as a plausible mid-K contender, and holding `EF=12`, `signum`, `LR=3.2e-3`, and `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` fixed isolates architecture as the only primary variable.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"16"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 31 exits minor-tweak exploitation due to severe stagnation and tests a fundamentally different family: `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` at `K=16, EF=12` under the exact settled low-K recipe for a clean architecture-only comparison."],"next_hypotheses":["If `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` wins at `K=16`, continue the same architecture-only comparison at `K=24` under the same recipe.","If it is close but slightly worse, keep the family incubating and test it at `K=24` before rejecting it.","If it clearly loses at `K=16`, return to `lowrank_two_stage_residual` and open a different substantial branch rather than more minor sweeps."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0238.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family: topk\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_i \u03b1_i b_i\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d {b_i} \u6765\u81ea\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ea\u505a\u5355\u6837\u672c top-k \u9009\u62e9\u4e0e\u7cfb\u6570\u8ba1\u7b97\uff0c\u90e8\u7f72\u4fa7\u4ecd\u662f\u5355\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 reference_round=r235 \u53ea\u6539\u4e00\u4e2a env \u53c2\u6570 `ARCHITECTURE=topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=signum`\u3001`LR=0.003`\u3001`AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125` \u53ca\u5176\u4f59\u914d\u7f6e\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5728\u8d85\u4f4e\u67e5\u8868\u9884\u7b97\u4e0b\uff0c\u6700\u77ed\u9009\u62e9\u94fe\u8def\u7684\u5355\u5e93 topk \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u7ea6 0.28x \u603b\u6210\u672c\u5904\u663e\u8457\u4f18\u4e8e\u5f53\u524d\u5de6\u7aef\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u70b9 `factorized_topk@0.30x` \u7684 FVU=0.3909\uff0c\u5e76\u8865\u51fa `<0.5x` Pareto \u524d\u6cbf\u5de6\u4fa7\u7f3a\u5931\u7684\u4e00\u679a\u66f4\u53ef\u7528\u70b9\u3002\u9009\u62e9\u8fd9\u4e00\u6b65\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u63a8\u8fdb `factorized_topk`\u3001`codebook_topk` \u6216 `topk@K248` \u7684 recipe \u5fae\u8c03\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a r237 \u5df2\u660e\u786e\u5426\u5b9a factorized scorer \u6269\u5bb9\u7ebf\uff0cr235 \u5df2\u660e\u786e\u5426\u5b9a\u5355 coarse codebook \u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u7ebf\uff0c\u800c r236 \u4e5f\u5df2\u5426\u5b9a\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5f3a topk \u951a\u70b9\u7684 LR \u5fae\u8c03\uff1b\u5728\u8fd9\u79cd\u60c5\u51b5\u4e0b\uff0c\u56de\u5230\u5c1a\u672a\u88ab\u5e72\u51c0\u56de\u7b54\u7684 `topk@EF1,K32` \u5de6\u7aef\u70b9\uff0c\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5c0f\u3001\u6700\u53ef\u89e3\u91ca\u4e14\u6700\u7b26\u5408 `<0.5x` \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u76ee\u6807\u7684\u52a8\u4f5c\u3002",
